%20door%20desks%20because%20it%20was%20the%20cheapest%20way%20we%20could%20support%20a%20desk.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20things%20that%20we%20do%20are%20scrappy%20by%20nature.%20So%20long%20as%20the%20scrappy%20solution%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20door%20desk%20has%20since%20become%20a%20symbol%20of%20Amazon's%20culture%20and%20its%20core%20value%20of%20frugality.%20A%20modern%20version%20of%20this%20design%20is%20still%20used%20across%20Amazon%20offices%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20the%202018%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-early-amazon-desk-recycled-door-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENetflix's%20first%20CEO%2C%20Marc%20Randolph%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%20previously%20said%20that%20Bezos%20told%20him%20that%20the%20makeshift%20desks%20were%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20message.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20way%20of%20saying%20that%20we%20spend%20money%20on%20things%20that%20affect%20our%20customers%2C%20not%20on%20things%20that%20don't%2C%26quot%3B%20Randolph%20recalled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20stepped%20down%20as%20Amazon's%20CEO%20in%202021%20and%20is%20currently%20the%20world's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fbillionaires%2Fprofiles%2Fjeffrey-p-bezos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esecond-richest%20person%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20%24184%20billion%20fortune.%20Bezos%20and%20Sanchez%20spent%20the%20summer%20of%202023%20sailing%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-yacht%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%24500%20million%20yacht%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20visiting%20various%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-jeff-bezos-amazon-uses-door-desk-from-early-days-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%