3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20decision%20didn't%20come%20out%20of%20the%20blue.%20When%20we%20first%20started%20dating%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20told%20me%20about%20his%20plans%20to%20move%20to%20Australia%20and%20travel.%20I%20just%20didn't%20realize%20it%20would%20come%20around%20so%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Esoon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20woman%20at%20the%20restaurant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b772996c8f0a134f7aa25c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFerlita%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20had%20been%20together%20for%20over%20two%20years%20when%20they%20moved%20to%20Australia.%3Cp%3EGabriella%20Ferlita%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20to%20choose%20between%20following%20my%20partner%2010%2C000%20miles%20from%20home%20or%20saying%20goodbye.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20a%20steady%2C%20full-time%20journalism%20job%20in%20London%20and%20wasn't%20in%20a%20position%20to%20leave.%20The%20stinging%20tears%20in%20my%20eyes%20confirmed%20what%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20say%3A%20the%20life%20we%20both%20knew%20would%20change%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFast%20forward%20three%20months%2C%20and%20I%20had%20left%20my%20job%20to%20freelance.%20After%20the%20late-night%20slogs%20on%20the%20news%20desk%2C%20I%20craved%20freedom.%20I%20wanted%20flexible%20working%20hours%2C%20to%20engage%20in%20journalism%20I%20truly%20believed%20in%2C%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ework%3Cspan%3E%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20partner%20had%20already%20asked%20me%20to%20join%20him%20in%20Australia%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20make%20the%20decision%20to%20move%20across%20the%20world%20based%20on%20feelings%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%