n%20to%20retire%20anytime%20soon%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EByrd's%20age%20is%20not%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20love%20people%20and%20they%20all%20treat%20me%20really%20nice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20station.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20I%20get%20up%20every%20morning%20and%20come%20to%20work%2C%20knowing%20that%20they%20are%20here%20and%20they%20know%20my%20name%20and%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EByrd%20even%20arrives%20an%20hour%20before%20her%20shifts%20start%20to%20help%20with%20setting%20up%2C%20KSWO%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDiscoverMedicineParkOK%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02Ws9eZjM1j3n8Mip5HPq3BDCRsYM3mPa5B5LCtY74FDf6fmSS4PrK9hy1eMNttqqkl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomments%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20local%20Facebook%20page%2C%20people%20praised%20Byrd%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20nicest%20people%20you%20will%20ever%20meet%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bsweetheart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20time%20they're%20understaffed%20(meaning%20she's%20having%20to%20work%20extra%20hard)%20but%20she%20is%20always%20there%20with%20a%20smile%20%26amp%3B%20a%20good%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Facebook%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EByrd%20told%20KSWO%20that%20in%202005%2C%20the%20burger%20chain%20gave%20her%20a%20Jeep%20to%20reward%20her%20for%20her%20speedy%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20avoids%20taking%20time%20off%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20love%20your%20job%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20be%20there%20no%20matter%20what%20and%20you%20know%20that's%20the%20way%20I%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20Byrd%20told%20KSWO.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20come%20to%20work%20sometimes%20sick%20or%20you%20know%20as%20far%20as%20hurting%2C%20because%20you%20know%20at%20my%20age%20you%20are%20going%20to%20hurt%2C%20so%20I%20do%20come%20to%20work%20anyway.%20I%20just%20get%20up%20anyway%20and%20come%20on%20to%20wo