nuary-29-todays-breaking-news-updates-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-pariksha-pe-charcha-124012900094_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Flatest-news-live-january-29-todays-breaking-news-updates-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-pariksha-pe-charcha-124012900094_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHas%20Never%20Been%20To%20NCA...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20Massive%20Praise%20For%20Virat%20Kohli%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20has%20hardly%20ever%20set%20foot%20at%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20for%20any%20fitness-related%20rehabilitation%20work%2C%20said%20Indian%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20who%20wants%20aspiring%20cricketers%20to%20follow%20the%20ace%20batter's%20exemplary%20work-ethic.%20%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20has%20never%20been%20to%20NCA%20in%20his%20entire%20career.%20I%20would%20say%20that%20all%20the%20younger%20players%20should%20look%20up%20to%20the%20passion%20that%20he%20has%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20told%20former%20India%20wicketkeeper%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20on%20JioCinema.%20%26quot%3BLeave%20alone%20how%20he%20plays%20the%20cover%20drive%2C%20flick%2C%20cut%20but%20first%20things%20first%20you%20have%20to%20understand%20what%20is%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20players%20that%20makes%20him%20where%20he%20is%20today.%26quot%3B%20Kohli%20has%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20of%20the%20ongoing%20five-match%20series%20against%20England%20for%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20reasons%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20watched%20Kohli%20enough.%20He%20can%20easily%20be%20satisfied%20with%20what%20he%20has%20achieved.%20He%20can%20say%20that%20I%20will%20take%20it%20easy%20in%20these%202-3%20series%2C%20I%20will%20come%20later%2C%20but%20he%20is%20always%20there%20for%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaying%20hungry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20skipper%20further%20emphasised%20the%20invaluable%20quality%20of%20hunger%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20complacency%20in%20Kohli's%20mindset%2C%20expressing%20that%20such%20attributes%20cannot%20be%20imparted%20through%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20aspiring%20cricketers%20to%20learn%20this%20internal%20drive%20by%20observing%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20mindset%20of%20being%20hungry%20and%20not%20complacent%20cannot%20be%20taught.%20You%20have%20to%20learn%20that%20from%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20others.%20It%20has%20to%20come%20from%20within.%20I%20cannot%20teach%20you%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20I%20would%20say%20rather%20than%20looking%20at%20Virat%20Kohli%20or%20others%20technically.%20You%20have%20to%20stay%20hungry%20all%20the%20time%2C%20bring%20the%20passion%20and%20the%20pride%20to%20everything%2C%20being%20out%20there%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20playing%20for%20the%20team%20and%20getting%20the%20job%20done.%20This%20is%20what%20I%20want%20to%20the%20guys%20to%20have%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20skipper%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706524740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbs6kptd_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-reuters-_625x300_25_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhas-never-been-to-nca-rohit-sharmas-massive-praise-for-virat-kohli-4947940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20has%20hardly%20ever%20set%20foot%20at%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20for%20any%20fitness-related%20rehabilitation%20work%2C%20said%20Indian%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maldives%20Opposition%20Moves%20To%20Impeach%20Pro-China%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20opposition%20party%20in%20Maldives%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20impeachment%20proceedings%20against%20its%20pro-China%20president%20Mohamed%20Muizzu.%20The%20main%20opposition%20party%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20holds%20a%20majority%20in%20parliament%20and%20the%20collection%20of%20signatures%20have%20already%20started%20to%20begin%20the%20impeachment%20filing.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20hit-out%20at%20President%20Muizzu%20for%20his%20pro-China%20position%20after%20a%20Chinese%20spy%20ship%20was%20granted%20permission%20by%20the%20government%20to%20dock%20in%20Male.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20scuffle%20took%20place%20in%20parliament%20yesterday%2C%20after%20which%20the%20Opposition%20decided%20to%20begin%20impeachment%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20vote%20on%20parliamentary%20approval%20for%20the%20Muizzu%20government%20was%20scheduled%20on%20Sunday%20and%20the%20violence%20started%20as%20the%20government%20MPs%20(PPM%2FPNC%20party)%20disturbed%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20weeks%2C%20President%20Muizzu%20who%20came%20to%20power%20with%20a%20distinctly%20anti-India%20position%2C%20has%20been%20facing%20pushback%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20diplomatic%20row%20with%20New%20Delhi%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20widely%20circulated%20post%20about%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Lakshadweep%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20ministers%20who%20made%20harsh%20comments%20were%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Muizzu's%20demand%20that%20India%20withdraw%20its%20troops%20stationed%20in%20the%20country%20by%20mid-March%20was%20the%20newest%20in%20the%20anti-India%20rhetoric%2C%20with%20the%20presence%20of%2080-odd%20Indian%20troops%20being%20portrayed%20as%20a%20security%20threat%20to%20the%20island%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20shift%20in%20policy%20--%20which%20traditionally%20held%20India%20as%20a%20friend%20and%20ally%20--%20did%20not%20sit%20well%20with%20the%20opposition%2C%20and%20matters%20escalated%20after%20the%20Chinese%20spy%20ship%20issue.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20or%20MDP%20and%20the%20Democrats%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bstark%26quot%3B%20anti-India%20pivot%20and%20issued%20a%20joint%20press%20statement%2C%20labelling%20the%20policy%20shift%20as%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20detrimental%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20country's%20long-term%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlienating%20any%20development%20partner%2C%20and%20especially%20the%20country's%20most%20long-standing%20ally%20will%20be%20extremely%20detrimental%20to%20the%20long-term%20development%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%20It%20also%20underscored%20that%20%26quot%3Bstability%20and%20security%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20is%20vital%20to%20the%20stability%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Maldives%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20MDP%20and%20the%20Democrats%20emphasised%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20consecutive%20governments%20to%20maintain%20the%20ability%20%26quot%3Bto%20work%20with%20all%20development%20partners%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Maldives%2C%20as%20the%20Maldives%20has%20traditionally%20done%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706524680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fc1nt5v2g_mohamed-muizzu_625x300_09_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaldives-opposition-moves-to-impeach-pro-china-president-mohamed-muizzu-4953524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20main%20opposition%20party%20in%20Maldives%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20impeachment%20proceedings%20against%20its%20pro-China%20president%20Mohamed%20Muizzu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A