20in%20north%20Delhi's%20Burari%20on%20January%202.%20The%20girl%20and%20her%20grandfather%20were%20out%20for%20a%20walk%20when%20the%20dog%20allegedly%20attacked%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20incidents%20involving%20stray%20dogs%20are%20being%20reported%20more%20often%20now%2C%20with%20videos%20causing%20alarm%20and%20leading%20to%20many%20housing%20complexes%20discouraging%20residents%20from%20feeding%20them%20inside%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20of%20several%20horrific%20attacks%20by%20pet%20dogs%20have%20also%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20concerned%20people%20calling%20for%20stricter%20guidelines%20to%20prevent%20such%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706524200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fu2clegfg_dog-attack_625x300_29_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fdog-attack-on-camera-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-child-in-ghaziabad-apartment-4953021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20yet%20another%20incident%20of%20the%20dog%20menace%2C%20a%20pack%20of%20stray%20dogs%20attacked%20a%20child%20in%20an%20apartment%20in%20Ghaziabad%20while%20he%20was%20playing%20putside%20in%20the%20compound%20area.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fdog-attack-on-camera-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-child-in-ghaziabad-apartment-4953021%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fdog-attack-on-camera-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-child-in-ghaziabad-apartment-4953021%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fdog-attack-on-camera-pack-of-stray-dogs-attack-child-in-ghaziabad-apartment-4953021%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20Bhatt%20steals%20hearts%20in%20a%20saree%20gown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706524200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstat