ian-producing-elizabeth-taylor-docuseries-1235890247%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fglobal%2Fkim-kardashian-producing-elizabeth-taylor-docuseries-1235890247%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20End%20Of%20The%20Road%20For%20The%20I.N.D.I.A%20Grouping%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20coalition%20was%20announced%20in%20July%202023%2C%20it%20raised%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20hope.%20Just%20two%20months%20before%2C%20in%20May%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20victory%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20results%20clearly%20demonstrated%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20its%20weaknesses.%20If%20the%20opposition%20parties%20played%20their%20cards%20right%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20be%20challenged.%20It%20was%20against%20this%20backdrop%20of%20hope%20that%20the%20grand%20coalition%20of%20opposition%20parties%20was%20launched.%20However%2C%20with%20just%20three%20months%20to%20the%20election%2C%20the%20alliance%20appears%20to%20be%20collapsing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%2C%20has%20reunited%20with%20the%20BJP%20-%20again%20-%20in%20Bihar%2C%20turning%20his%20back%20on%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%20and%20his%20ambition%20to%20defeat%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%20coming%20election.%20The%20man%20of%20multiple%20u-turns%20has%20dealt%20a%20body%20blow%20to%20the%20hopes%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20especially%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2024%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20fired%20the%20first%20shot%20by%20stating%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20would%20fight%20the%20election%20alone%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20This%20was%20soon%20followed%20by%20the%20AAP%2C%20which%20announced%20a%20solo%20fight%20in%20Punjab.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20AAP%20announcements%20do%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20grouping%20has%20multiple%20ideological%20and%20political%20contradictions%2C%20which%20were%20bound%20to%20surface%20at%20some%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20underpinning%20logic%20of%20forming%20the%20alliance%20was%20simple.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20got%20a%20pan-India%20vote%20share%20of%2037.3%25.%20The%20non-BJP%20vote%20across%20India%20account%20for%20just%20below%2063%25.%20If%20this%2063%25%20went%20to%20just%20one%20opposition%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20be%20stopped.%20The%20BJP%20was%20winning%20because%20the%20opposition%20vote%20was%20divided.%20Arithmetically%2C%20there%20is%20sense%20in%20this%20argument.%20It%20is%20a%20simple%20case%20of%20ensuring%20the%20non-BJP%20vote%20comes%20to%20just%20one%20single%20party.%20While%20there%20is%20simple%20math%20behind%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20grouping%2C%20the%20electoral%20realities%20are%20not%20so%20simple.%20There%20are%20two%20challenges%20that%20neutralize%20the%20arithmetic.%20First%2C%20there%20is%20a%20fundamental%20difference%20between%20arithmetic%20and%20chemistry.%20Pre-poll%20coalitions%20are%20not%20formed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20arithmetic%20convenience%20but%20rather%20on%20chemistry%20and%20ideological%20compatibility.%20Secondly%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20there%20are%20important%20ideological%20and%20political%20contradictions%20between%20the%20numerous%20parties%20within%20the%20alliance.%20The%20Trinamool%20and%20AAP's%20decision%20to%20contest%20alone%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20these%20fundamental%20contradictions%20coming%20to%20the%20surface.%20I%20will%20discuss%20both%20these%20points%20in%20further%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20pre-poll%20alliances%20like%20I.N.D.I.A%20are%20formed%2C%20the%20parties%20involved%20hold%20out%20the%20hope%20that%20their%20votes%20are%20transferable%20to%20their%20alliance%20partners.%20If%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20BSP%20and%20Congress%20put%20up%20one%20single%20candidate%20from%20the%20SP%2C%20the%20idea%20is%20that%20Congress%20and%20BSP%20voters%20from%20that%20constituency%20would%20also%20switch%20over%20to%20the%20SP.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20always%20the%20case.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202019%2C%20the%20SP%20and%20BSP%20alliance%20appeared%20to%20have%20worked.%20The%20SP%20and%20BSP%20votes%20were%20transferable%20and%20the%20BJP%20lost%20some%20seats%20they%20had%20won%20in%202014.%20The%20same%20logic%20did%20not%20work%20in%20Karnataka%20in%202019%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20(JDS)%20fought%20together.%20Here%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2026%20out%20of%20the%2028%20seats%2C%20a%20big%20improvement%20from%202014%2C%20when%20it%20won%2017.%20The%20success%20of%20pre-poll%20alliances%20relies%20on%20more%20than%20just%20arithmetic.%20Chemistry%20is%20a%20very%20important%20factor.%20While%20leaders%20may%20coordinate%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20is%20there%20a%20similar%20level%20of%20synergy%20there%20amongst%20cadres%20on%20the%20ground%3F%20If%20this%20chemistry%20is%20absent%2C%20the%20alliance%20is%20likely%20to%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20fallout%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20is%20also%20an%20indication%20of%20fundamental%20contradictions.%20In%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool%20and%20CPM%20are%20bitter%20political%20rivals.%20Would%20the%20three%20parties%20set%20aside%20their%20contradicting%20political%20interests%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20common%20seat%20sharing%20formula%3F%20Recent%20developments%20suggest%20that%20is%20clearly%20not%20the%20case.%20Though%20there%20was%20a%20fragile%20truce%20until%20now%2C%20the%20differences%20erupted%20when%20the%20question%20of%20seat%20sharing%20came%20up.%20A%20similar%20story%20plays%20out%20in%20Punjab.%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20political%20rivals%20in%20the%20state.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20very%20small%20electoral%20presence%20in%20Punjab.%20It%20made%20no%20sense%20to%20AAP%20to%20agree%20on%20a%20seat%20sharing%20formula%20in%20Punjab%2C%20a%20state%20where%20they%20are%20the%20primary%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20these%20differing%20political%20interests%2C%20there%20are%20fundamental%20ideological%20differences%20too.%20The%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20exposed%20these%20ideological%20differences.%20The%20Trinamool%20and%20Left%20Parties%20have%20taken%20a%20clear-cut%20stance%20on%20the%20issue.%20Sitaram%20Yechury's%20visit%20to%20Lenin's%20statue%20firmly%20underscores%20the%20Left's%20commitment%20to%20politics%20devoid%20of%20any%20involvement%20with%20religious%20identities.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20not%20distanced%20herself%20from%20religion%20but%20highlighted%20the%20need%20to%20engage%20with%20all%20faiths%20equally.%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20AAP%20have%20indicated%20a%20move%20towards%20'soft'%20Hindutva%2C%20positioning%20the%20party%20as%20a%20right-of-centre%20alternative%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Following%20AAP's%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20alliance%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20proclaimed%20that%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20was%20a%20'matter%20of%20pride'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20now%20just%20a%20few%20months%20away%2C%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20coalition%20seems%20to%20be%20unravelling%20at%20the%20worst%20possible%20time.%20The%20friction%20should%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20There%20are%20fundamental%20internal%20contradictions%20between%20various%20partners%2C%20which%20are%20blowing%20up%20during%20discussions%20on%20seat%20sharing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20coalition%20manages%20to%20navigate%20these%20challenges%20will%20be%20crucial.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20India%20coalition%20has%20its%20work%20cut%20out.%20Following%20the%20December%20election%20results%20and%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20the%20momentum%20appears%20to%20be%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20author%20is%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Humanities%20and%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20GITAM%20Deemed%20to%20be%20University%2C%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706523900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftg2n9v3g_india-alliance-mumbai-meeting-650_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fend-of-the-road-for-the-i-n-d-i-a-grouping-4953290%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20grouping%20has%20multiple%20ideological%20and%20political%20contradictions%2C%20which%20were%20bound%20to%20surface%20at%20some%20point.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fend-of-the-road-for-the-i-n-d-i-a-grouping-4953290%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fend-of-the-road-for-the-i-n-d-i-a-grouping-4953290%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fend-of-the-road-for-the-i-n-d-i-a-grouping-4953290%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%203%20big%20reasons%20Americans%20are%20suddenly%20psyched%20about%20the%20economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20collage%20featuring%20images%20of%20a%20person%20in%20a%20factory%20carrying%20stacks%20of%20eggs%2C%20a%20fuel%20price%20display%2C%20and%20an%20upward-trending%20line%20on%20stocks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b4138a43bb77284ba0e39f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmerican%20consumers%20are%20starting%20to%20feel%20less%20terrible%20about%20the%20economy%20thanks%20to%20three%20things%3A%20gas%20price