verage%20for%20a%20gallon%20is%20%243.096%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgasprices.aaa.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAAA%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20compared%20to%20%243.446%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20down%20from%20a%20record%20high%20of%20over%20%245%20in%202022.%20Gas%20prices%20are%20an%20economic%20reality%20that%20hits%20consumers%20especially%20hard.%20You%20can't%20choose%20to%20skip%20work%20or%20refuse%20to%20take%20your%20kids%20to%20school%20just%20because%20prices%20at%20the%20pump%20are%20killing%20you.%20Plus%2C%20there's%20the%20fact%20that%20America's%20public-transportation%20system%20is%2C%20um%2C%20lacking.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.mit.edu%2Frest%2Farticle-abstract%2F104%2F2%2F293%2F97647%2FStuck-in-the-Seventies-Gas-Prices-and-Consumer%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EResearch%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D2034408%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshows%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20consumers%20feel%20more%20pessimistic%20when%20gas%20prices%20go%20up%20%E2%80%94%20James%20Surowiecki%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fideas%2Farchive%2F2023%2F12%2Fwhy-gas-prices-falling-inflation%2F676381%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epoints%20out%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20The%20Atlantic%20that%20high%20gas%20prices%20also%20make%20people%20less%20happy%20and%20more%20likely%20to%20hate%20the%20president.%20If%20oil%20prices%20stay%20relatively%20low%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20keep%20gas%20prices%20down%2C%20less%20exasperated%20drivers%20could%20help%20Joe%20Biden%20keep%20his%20job%20come%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20brings%20us%20to%20eggs.%20I%20know%20it%20seems%20a%20little%20weird%20to%20peg%20consumer%20confidence%20to%20something%20so%20mundane%20and%20seemingly%20inconsequential%2C%20but%20hear%20me%20out%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22ht