20improving%20living%20standards%2C%20and%20fostering%20sustainable%20expansion.%20Classical%20and%20neoclassical%20theories%20highlight%20the%20importance%20of%20infrastructure%20in%20increasing%20the%20productive%20capacity%20of%20an%20economy%2C%20as%20efficient%20transportation%2C%20communication%20networks%2C%20and%20energy%20distribution%20systems%20reduce%20operational%20costs%20and%20enhance%20competitiveness.%20Meanwhile%2C%20endogenous%20growth%20theory%20emphasizes%20the%20role%20of%20infrastructure%20investments%20in%20promoting%20technological%20innovation%20and%20human%20capital%20development%2C%20with%20education%20and%20research%20facilities%20sparking%20innovations%20that%20propel%20growth.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20new%20economic%20geography%20underscores%20infrastructure's%20significance%20in%20connecting%20remote%20areas%20with%20economic%20hubs%2C%20facilitating%20regional%20development%2C%20and%20ensuring%20more%20balanced%20economic%20growth%20across%20different%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20sustainable%20economic%20advancement%2C%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20infrastructure%20projects%20with%20high%20multiplier%20effects%2C%20such%20as%20transportation%20networks%2C%20renewable%20energy%20sources%2C%20water%20and%20sanitation%20systems%2C%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20educational%20and%20health%20facilities.%20These%20investments%20not%20only%20provide%20immediate%20employment%20opportunities%20and%20stimulate%20economic%20demand%20but%20also%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20for%20future%20prosperity%20by%20boosting%20efficiency%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20human%20capital.%20Such%20strategic%20infrastructure%20development%20is%20essential%20for%20achieving%20long-term%20economic%20objectives%2C%20as%20it%20not%20only%20meets%20immediate%20needs%20but%20also%20addresses%20future%20challenges%20and%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20critique%20of%20short-term%2C%20inefficient%20investments%2C%20illustrated%20by%20Keynes'%20metaphor%20of%20%26quot%3Bdigging%20holes%20and%20filling%20them%20up%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20underscores%20the%20necessity%20of%20prioritizing%20projects%20that%20yield%20substantial%20and%20enduring%20economic%20benefits.%20While%20Keynes%20advocated%20for%20government%20spending%20to%20stimulate%20demand%20during%20downturns%2C%20he%20cautioned%20against%20wasteful%20expenditures.%20Instead%2C%20the%20emphasis%20should%20be%20on%20sustainable%20infrastructure%20projects%20that%20not%20only%20provide%20a%20short-term%20economic%20boost%20but%20also%20contribute%20to%20long-term%20growth%20by%20enhancing%20the%20overall%20productivity%20and%20competitiveness%20of%20the%20economy.%20This%20approach%20aligns%20with%20broader%20economic%20theories%20that%20stress%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20strategic%20infrastructure%20investment%20in%20supporting%20long-term%20development%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20equitable%20regional%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20precisely%20what%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20done.%20Since%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20office%20in%202014%2C%20infrastructure%20development%20has%20been%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20government's%20economic%20strategy%2C%20significantly%20impacting%20India's%20growth%20trajectory.%20The%20Modi%20administration%20has%20prioritized%20large-scale%20infrastructure%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20development%20of%20highways%2C%20railways%2C%20airports%2C%20smart%20cities%2C%20and%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20enhancing%20connectivity%2C%20improving%20efficiency%2C%20and%20attracting%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202023%2C%20the%20national%20highway%20network%20had%20increased%20by%2060%25%20from%20its%20extent%20in%202014%2C%20showcasing%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20infrastructure%20development.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20length%20of%20national%20highways%20increased%20from%2091%2C287%20km%20in%202014%20to%20146%2C145%20km%20by%202023.%20The%20pace%20of%20construction%20has%20been%20noteworthy%2C%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20maintaining%20a%20construction%20pace%20of%2020.78%20km%20per%20day%20during%20the%20first%20seven%20months%20of%20the%20financial%20year%202023-24.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20initiative%20to%20construct%2012%2C500%20km%20of%20highways%20within%20the%20year.%20For%20context%2C%20the%20annual%20highway%20construction%20achievements%20in%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202023%20included%2010%2C237%20km%20in%202019-20%2C%2013%2C327%20km%20in%202020-21%2C%20and%2010%2C457%20km%20in%202021-22.%20This%20marked%20increase%20in%20highway%20construction%20under%20the%20Modi%20government%20contrasts%20with%20the%20pace%20before%202014%2C%20indicating%20a%20robust%20focus%20on%20building%20infrastructure%20as%20a%20means%20to%20bolster%20economic%20growth%20and%20connectivity%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20efforts%20are%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20Bharatmala%20Pariyojana%2C%20an%20ambitious%20program%20aimed%20at%20developing%20about%2034%2C800%20km%20of%20highways%20across%20India.%20The%20initiative%20reflects%20the%20government's%20strategy%20to%20improve%20transportation%2C%20facilitate%20trade%2C%20and%20enhance%20accessibility%2C%20thereby%20contributing%20to%20the%20nation's%20socio-economic%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20since%202014%2C%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20journey%2C%20marked%20by%20significant%20increases%20in%20capital%20expenditure%20and%20ambitious%20modernization%20efforts.%20The%20period%20has%20seen%20record%20investments%20in%20railway%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20the%20rollout%20of%20modern%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20trains%2C%20accelerated%20station%20redevelopment%20under%20the%20Amrit%20Bharat%20scheme%2C%20and%20a%20notable%20push%20towards%20electrification%20and%20track%20laying.%20The%20Gross%20Budgetary%20Support%20(GBS)%20for%20the%20railways%20saw%20a%20quantum%20leap%20in%202023-24%2C%20reaching%20Rs%202.4%20lakh%20crore%2C%20highlighting%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20enhancing%20the%20rail%20network's%20capacity%20and%20efficiency.%20This%20investment%20is%20a%20substantial%20increase%20from%20previous%20years%2C%20demonstrating%20a%20strategic%20focus%20on%20leveraging%20the%20railways%20to%20drive%20economic%20growth%20and%20improve%20connectivity%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20period%20before%202014%2C%20under%20the%20UPA%20government%2C%20saw%20more%20modest%20investments%20in%20railway%20infrastructure.%20The%20GBS%20in%20the%20railway%20budget%20for%202004-05%20was%20Rs%208%2C000%20crore%2C%20and%20for%202013-14%20it%20was%20Rs%2029%2C055%20crore%2C%20indicating%20a%20more%20conservative%20approach%20to%20railway%20development.%20The%20Modi%20government's%20approach%20marks%20a%20significant%20departure%20from%20the%20past%2C%20focusing%20not%20just%20on%20expanding%20the%20rail%20network%20but%20also%20on%20modernizing%20it%20with%20advanced%20technology%20and%20services.%20This%20includes%20the%20extensive%20rollout%20of%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%2C%20which%20are%20indigenously%20designed%20semi-high%20speed%20trains%2C%20and%20the%20fast-tracking%20of%20major%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20the%20redevelopment%20of%20stations%20and%20the%20laying%20of%20new%20tracks.%20The%20emphasis%20on%20modernization%20and%20high-capacity%20infrastructure%20reflects%20a%20strategic%20shift%20towards%20making%20Indian%20Railways%20a%20world-class%20transporter%2C%20ready%20to%20meet%20the%20future%20demands%20of%20a%20rapidly%20growing%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20union%20government%20is%20also%20addressing%20the%20regional%20infrastructure%20development%20disparity.%20Since%202014%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20significantly%20increased%20infrastructure%20development%20in%20the%20North%20Eastern%20Region%20(NER)%2C%20marking%20a%20substantial%20shift%20from%20the%20initiatives%20undertaken%20prior%20to%202014%20under%20the%20UPA%20government.%20An%20impressive%20sum%20of%20Rs.%203.84%20lakh%20crore%20has%20been%20allocated%20by%2055%20non-exempted%20Central%20Ministries%2FDepartments%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20NER%2C%20including%20Assam%2C%20leveraging%20at%20least%2010%25%20of%20their%20Gross%20Budgetary%20Support%20(GBS)%20for%20this%20purpose.%20This%20expenditure%20has%20facilitated%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20projects%2C%20from%20road%20construction%2C%20where%204%2C121%20km%20of%20road%20projects%20have%20been%20completed%2C%20to%20the%20sanctioning%20of%20Rs.%2019%2C855%20crore%20for%20new%20rail%20projects%2C%20enhancing%20both%20road%20and%20rail%20connectivity%20in%20the%20region.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20telecommunications%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20bolstered%20with%20the%20installation%20of%201%2C358%20towers%20covering%201%2C246%20villages%2C%20and%201%2C195%20projects%20worth%20Rs.%2015%2C375%20crore%20have%20been%20sanctioned%20under%20the%20schemes%20of%20MDoNER%20and%20NEC%20in%20the%20NER%20States%2C%20including%20Assam%2C%20from%202014-2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20contrasts%20starkly%20with%20the%20period%20before%202014%2C%20where%20infrastructure%20development%20in%20the%20NER%20was%20less%20pronounced%20and%20less%20integrated.%20The%20comprehensive%20and%20multi-modal%20nature%20of%20the%20projects%20initiated%20since%202014-encompassing%20road%2C%20rail%2C%20air%2C%20waterway%2C%20telecom%2C%20and%20power%20connectivity-reflects%20a%20more%20holistic%20and%20concerted%20effort%20to%20bring%20the%20NER%20into%20the%20mainstream%20of%20national%20development.%20The%20focus%20has%20not%20only%20been%20on%20enhancing%20connectivity%20but%20also%20on%20ensuring%20that%20these%20infrastructure%20developments%20are%20sustainable%20and%20cater%20to%20the%20long-term%20needs%20of%20the%20region%2C%20thus%20setting%20a%20new%20precedent%20for%20focused%20regional%20development%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20power%20sector%2C%20India%20has%20made%20remarkable%20strides%2C%20transitioning%20from%20a%20power%20deficit%20to%20a%20power%20surplus%20nation.%20The%20average%20availability%20of%20power%20has%20significantly%20improved%2C%20reaching%2020.5%20hours%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%2023.5%20hours%20in%20urban%20areas.%20This%20achievement%20is%20poised%20to%20make%20generating%20sets%20and%20stabilizers%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20Additionally%2C%20India%20has%20become%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20the%20cost-effective%20production%20of%20renewable%20energy%2C%20boasting%20the%20cheapest%20renewable%20energy%20production%20costs%20worldwide.%20This%20focus%20on%20renewable%20energy%20is%20part%20of%20India's%20broader%20commitment%20to%20sustainable%20development%20and%20energy%20security.%20The%20nation%20has%20achieved%20its%20NDC%20target%20of%20having%2040%25%20of%20its%20installed%20electricity%20capacity%20from%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources%20nine%20years%20ahead%20of%20schedule%2C%20in%202021.%20This%20achievement%20underscores%20India's%20commitment%20to%20combating%20climate%20change%20and%20transitioning%20towards%20a%20green%20economy.%20The%20rapid%20expansion%20in%20solar%20capacity%2C%20which%20has%20increased%2023-fold%20since%202014%2C%20along%20with%20the%20distribution%20of%20nearly%2090%20lakh%20solar%20lighting%20systems%2C%20reflects%20the%20government's%20focus%20on%20harnessing%20solar%20energy%20to%20meet%20its%20power%20needs.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20deployment%20of%20over%205.3%20lakh%20solar%20pumps%20to%20farmers%20signifies%20a%20push%20towards%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices.%20The%20reduction%20in%20solar%20tariffs%20to%20below%20Rs.%202%20per%20unit%20highlights%20the%20economic%20viability%20of%20renewable%20energy%2C%20making%20it%20an%20attractive%20investment%20and%20further%20driving%20India's%20renewable%20energy%20sector%20forward.%20This%20concerted%20push%20towards%20renewable%20energy%20is%20a%20key%20component%20of%20India's%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20aligning%20with%20global%20sustainability%20goals%20and%20ensuring%20energy%20security%20for%20future%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20notable%20advancements%20in%20power%20and%20transportation%20infrastructure%2C%20India's%20focus%20on%20telecommunications%20and%20digital%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20transformative.%20The%20government's%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%20a%20drastic%20reduction%20in%20mobile%20data%20tariffs%2C%20from%20Rs%20269%20per%20GB%20in%202014%20to%20Rs%2010.1%20per%20GB%2C%20making%20digital%20connectivity%20more%20accessible%20to%20a%20broader%20segment%20of%20the%20population.%20This%20reduction%20in%20costs%20has%20spurred%20a%20remarkable%20increase%20in%20data%20consumption%2C%20which%20has%20grown%2063%20times%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20mobile%20broadband%20subscribers%20has%20expanded%20more%20than%2017%20times.%20Such%20developments%20are%20pivotal%20in%20driving%20India's%20digital%20revolution%2C%20making%20information%20and%20digital%20services%20more%20accessible%20and%20fostering%20inclusive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20infrastructure%20development%20under%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20reflects%20a%20strategic%20vision%20to%20transform%20India%20into%20a%20developed%20nation%20with%20future-ready%20infrastructure.%20This%20vision%20encompasses%20not%20just%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20but%20also%20the%20digital%20and%20energy%20landscapes%2C%20ensuring%20that%20India's%20growth%20is%20sustainable%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20resilient.%20The%20government's%20concerted%20efforts%20in%20these%20areas%20are%20setting%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20new%20era%20of%20prosperity%20and%20global%20competitiveness%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBibek%20Debroy%20is%20the%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20%26amp%3B%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20Additional%20Private%20Secretary%20(Policy%20%26amp%3B%20Research)%2C%20EAC-PM.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706520600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F4l4i1e1g_narendra-modi-ani_625x300_03_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcharting-the-course-of-infrastructure-transformation-in-the-modi-era-4671928%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infrastructure%20development%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20driving%20long-term%20economic%20growth%20by%20enhancing%20productivity%2C%20improving%20living%20standards%2C%20and%20fostering%20sustainable%20expansion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcharting-the-course-of-infrastructure-transformation-in-the-modi-era-4671928%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcharting-the-course-of-infrastructure-transformation-in-the-modi-era-4671928%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcharting-the-course-of-infrastructure-transformation-in-the-modi-era-4671928%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Security%20up%20as%20Maldivian%20Oppn%20readies%20impeachment%20motion%20against%20Prez%20Muizzu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706519844000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107231343%2Cimgsize-1206830.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fpro-china-maldivian-president-mohamed-muizzu-likely-to-face-impeachment-soon%2Farticleshow%2F107227132.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pro-China%20Maldivian%20president%20is%20likely%20to%20face%20impeachment%20proceedings%20as%20the%20main%