-budget-2024-india-likely-to-register-7-economic-growth-in-fy25-124012900369_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Funion-budget-2024-india-likely-to-register-7-economic-growth-in-fy25-124012900369_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Funion-budget-2024-india-likely-to-register-7-economic-growth-in-fy25-124012900369_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Strong%20Political%20Message%20Behind%20Macron's%20India%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20Emmanuel%20Macron's%20visit%20to%20India%20as%20chief%20guest%20at%20our%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20had%20a%20ceremonial%20aspect%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20but%20in%20relations%20between%20states%20ceremonial%20gestures%20convey%20a%20message%20at%20many%20levels%20-%20of%20an%20honour%20deserved%2C%20importance%20of%20the%20relationship%2C%20an%20investment%20into%20the%20future%2C%20expected%20benefits%2C%20a%20signal%20to%20others%2C%20and%20the%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20f%C3%AAted%20by%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20June%202023%2C%20it%20conveyed%20a%20strong%20political%20message%20at%20the%20bilateral%20and%20international%20levels%2C%20of%20the%20US%20wooing%20India%20for%20larger%20strategic%20goals.%20Ceremony%20is%20part%20of%20diplomacy%20and%20is%20not%20without%20substance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20himself%20was%20Guest%20of%20Honour%20on%20Bastille%20Day%20(July%2014)%20in%20Paris%20in%202023.%20That%20honour%20was%20to%20convey%20France's%20desire%20to%20build%20stronger%20all-round%20ties%20with%20India.%20It%20was%20an%20investment%20in%20the%20future%20in%20view%20of%20India's%20growing%20economy%2C%20its%20diplomatic%20prowess%2C%20and%20shared%20strategic%20interests%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20in%20particular.%20Building%20more%20common%20ground%20with%20India%20on%20climate%20change%20issues%2C%20which%20is%20a%20prime%20area%20of%20debate%20and%20concern%20in%20French%20society%20(Modi%20and%20Macron%20reaffirmed%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%20their%20commitment%20to%20come%20forward%20in%20their%20next%20nationally%20determined%20contributions%20with%20ambitious%20targets%2C%20with%20France%20commending%20India's%20offer%20to%20host%20COP%2033%20in%202028)%20is%20an%20important%20French%20objective.%20So%20is%20leveraging%20French%20capabilities%20to%20foster%20links%20with%20increasing%20Indian%20capabilities%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20defence%2C%20advanced%20technologies%20and%20the%20digital%20domain%2C%20using%20India%20as%20a%20springboard%20for%20reaching%20out%20more%20to%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20which%20is%20becoming%20more%20vocal%20and%20demanding%20with%20regard%20to%20its%20interests%20in%20the%20hitherto%20west-dominated%20global%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20India%20drawing%20closer%20to%20the%20US%20and%20its%20Quad%20membership%2C%20France%2C%20which%20has%20major%20interests%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20seeks%20to%20carve%20out%20an%20independent%20role%20for%20itself%20and%20not%20let%20itself%20be%20subsumed%20under%20US-led%20structures.%20This%2C%20to%20mark%20its%20attachment%20to%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B.%20In%20pursuing%20this%2C%20India%20is%20an%20obvious%20partner.%20For%20India%20too%2C%20a%20closer%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20France%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20is%20diplomatically%20important%20as%20it%20conveys%20the%20message%20that%20security%20concerns%20in%20this%20region%20are%20also%20shared%20by%20a%20major%20European%20power%2C%20and%20not%20US%2C%20Australia%20and%20Japan%20alone.%20In%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region's%20significance%20for%20the%20respective%20sovereign%20and%20strategic%20interests%20of%20France%20and%20India%20has%20been%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20says%20explicitly%2C%20%26quot%3BDefense%20and%20security%20partnership%20has%20been%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20India-France%20partnership%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20meaningful%2C%20as%20the%20security%20threat%20in%20this%20region%20emanates%20from%20China.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20his%20banquet%20speech%2C%20Macron%20referred%20to%20the%20activities%20of%20%26quot%3Bsome%20hegemonic%20powers%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20The%20two%20sides%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20intensify%20their%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Southwest%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20building%20on%20the%20joint%20surveillance%20missions%20carried%20out%20from%20La%20Reunion%20in%202020%20and%202022.%20Significantly%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20extend%20those%20interactions%20in%20India's%20maritime%20neighbourhood%20to%20contribute%20positively%20to%20the%20securitisation%20of%20strategic%20sea%20lanes%20of%20communication.%20The%20two%20sides%20have%20also%20committed%20to%20revitalizing%20the%20trilateral%20cooperation%20with%20Australia%2C%20deepen%20the%20one%20with%20UAE%2C%20and%20explore%20new%20ones%20in%20the%20region.%20They%20have%20agreed%20to%20explore%20opportunities%20for%20coordinating%20economic%20projects%20and%20programmes%20in%20the%20Pacific%2C%20which%20marks%20an%20extension%20of%20India's%20role%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20notes%20that%20%26quot%3Bsince%20the%20declaration%20of%20the%20Strategic%20Partnership%20in%201998%2C%20India%20and%20France%20have%20developed%20a%20partnership%20of%20exceptional%20trust%20and%20confidence%2C%20consistency%20and%20strength%26quot%3B.%20The%20word%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%26quot%3B%20is%20noteworthy.%20The%20references%20to%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20shared%20commitment%20to%20a%20multipolar%20world%26quot%3B%20may%20seem%20predictable%20phrases%2C%20but%20they%20do%20convey%20the%20desire%20of%20both%20sides%20to%20exercise%20some%20independence%20at%20the%20strategic%20level%2C%20consonant%20with%20their%20national%20interests.%20Macron%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20of%20the%20view%20that%20US%20policy%20on%20Taiwan%20is%20needlessly%20provocative%20and%20that%20France%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20a%20camp%20follower%20of%20the%20US%20in%20such%20questionable%20policies.%20This%20implies%20that%20France%20understands%20India's%20decision%20to%20protect%20its%20strategic%20ties%20with%20Russia%20even%20though%20France%20itself%20is%20increasingly%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20Moscow%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20The%20wording%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%20is%20careful%20and%20does%20not%20depart%20from%20the%20established%20Indian%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commitment%20to%20a%20multipolar%20world%20has%20been%20expressed%20by%20India%20and%20France%20over%20the%20years.%20For%20France%20it%20means%20a%20world%20that%20is%20not%20dominated%20entirely%20by%20the%20US%20and%20one%20in%20which%20Europe%20plays%20a%20strategic%20role%2C%20separate%20from%20the%20US%20based%20on%20its%20own%20priorities%20and%20interests%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20US%20when%20required.%20For%20India%2C%20multipolarity%20is%20essential%20for%20global%20rebalancing%2C%20to%20achieve%20UN%2C%20IMF%20and%20World%20Bank%20reforms%2C%20and%20for%20giving%20more%20weight%20to%20developing%20countries%20in%20international%20governance.%20India%20joins%20the%20BRICS%20and%20the%20SCO%20is%20support%20of%20multipolarity%20with%20this%20objective.%20India%2C%20of%20course%2C%20emphasises%20multipolarity%20in%20Asia%20as%20an%20essential%20step%20towards%20a%20multipolar%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20affirms%20France's%20support%20for%20India's%20candidacy%20to%20the%20International%20Energy%20Agency.%20The%20two%20countries%20have%20agreed%20to%20institute%20a%20Comprehensive%20Dialogue%20on%20Global%20Issues.%20The%20urgent%20need%20for%20the%20reform%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20and%20the%20early%20commencement%20of%20text-based%20negotiations%20at%20the%20Intergovernmental%20Negotiations%20(IGN)%20in%20the%20UN%20figures%20in%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%20has%20congratulated%20Modi%20for%20his%20leadership%20in%20launching%20the%20historic%20initiative%20of%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Corridor%20(IMEC)%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%20in%20September%202023.%20Modi%20has%20welcomed%20the%20appointment%20of%20President%20Macron's%20Special%20Envoy%20for%20the%20project%2C%20though%20this%20project%20will%20have%20to%20be%20shelved%20for%20the%20time%20being%20in%20view%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%20While%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20the%20two%20have%20condemned%20the%20huge%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%2C%20and%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20respect%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20and%20to%20create%20conditions%2C%20including%20through%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%2C%20for%20aid%20to%20flow%20to%20the%20affected%20population%20in%20the%20Gaza%20region.%20Both%20leaders%20have%20reaffirmed%20that%20a%20political%20process%20leading%20to%20a%20two-state%20solution%20for%20the%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20people%20is%20required%20for%20lasting%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20the%20region%2C%20besides%20expressing%20grave%20concern%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20further%20expansion%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20the%20region%2C%20including%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20has%20always%20been%20a%20vital%20part%20of%20India-France%20ties%2C%20going%20back%20to%20the%201950s.%20Cynics%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20say%20that%20France%20dresses%20up%20its%20ties%20with%20India%20with%20the%20sole%20purpose%20of%20selling%20more%20arms.%20This%20supposes%20that%20India%20has%20little%20agency%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20is%20manipulated%20into%20buying%20French%20defence%20equipment.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20India%20sees%20France%20as%20a%20valuable%20defence%20partner%2C%20increasingly%20willing%20to%20transfer%20technology%2C%20one%20that%20has%20never%20applied%20sanctions%20on%20India%20or%20attached%20conditions%20to%20arms%20sales%2C%20besides%20the%20fact%20that%20its%20defence%20products%20are%20of%20high%20quality%2C%20though%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20lauds%20the%20all-round%20progress%20in%20defence%20and%20security%20partnership%2C%20which%20is%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20principal%20pillar%20of%20the%20partnership%20and%20a%20source%20of%20strengthening%20their%20countries'%20sovereignty%20and%20strategic%20autonomy%26quot%3B.%20It%20extends%20from%20intelligence%20and%20information%20exchange%20to%20exercises%20and%20equipment%20and%20across%20all%20domains%20from%20the%20seabed%20to%20space.%20Macron%20and%20Modihave%20reiterated%20their%20commitment%20to%20further%20deepening%20the%20integration%20between%20the%20two%20countries'%20respective%20defence%20industrial%20sectors%20and%20to%20work%20together%20to%20identify%20opportunities%20for%20co-design%2C%20co-development%2C%20co-production%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20not%20only%20fulfilling%20the%20defence%20needs%20of%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%2C%20but%20also%20of%20providing%20a%20viable%20and%20reliable%20source%20of%20defence%20supplies%20to%20other%20friendly%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20this%20end%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20welcomed%20the%20adoption%20of%20an%20ambitious%20Defence%20Industrial%20Roadmap.%20The%20exact%20content%20of%20this%20roadmap%20has%20not%20been%20divulged%2C%20but%20it%20appears%20that%20it%20opens%20the%20door%20to%20ambitious%20collaborations%20in%20sensitive%20areas.%20It%20includes%20plans%20to%20add%20MRO%20for%20Rafale%20engines%2C%20a%20comprehensive%20helicopter%20partnership%20with%20a%20Joint%20Venture%20for%20IMRH%20engine%20between%20HAL%20and%20Safran%2C%20and%20the%20Scorpene%20submarines%20constructed%20in%20India%2C%20including%20indigenisation.%20India's%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20the%20French%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Armament%20(DGA)%20intend%20to%20conclude%20an%20Arrangement%20MoU%20in%20an%20early%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20space%2C%20the%20co-development%2C%20manufacture%20and%20launch%20of%20satellites%20and%20payloads%2C%20research%20in%20new%20launch%20vehicle%20technologies%20and%20reusable%20launch%20vehicles%20and%20connecting%20the%20startups%20and%20users%20in%20both%20countries%20are%20envisaged.%20The%20MoU%20between%20NSIL%20and%20Arianespace%20is%20intended%20to%20build%20a%20long-term%20partnership%20on%20satellite%20launch%20missions.%20Modi%20and%20Macron%20have%20also%20welcomed%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Letter%20of%20Intent%20on%20Defence%20Space%20Cooperation%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20very%20substantial%20military%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Jaitapur%20Nuclear%20Power%20Plant%20Project%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20very%20high%20unit%20cost%20seems%20almost%20intractable.%20The%20French%20side%20wanted%20some%20positive%20move%20towards%20implementation%20but%20India%20was%20reluctant%20to%20invest%20more%20funds%20in%20proposed%20mechanisms%20to%20that%20end.%20Eventually%2C%20as%20a%20compromise%20language%2C%20it%20has%20been%20agreed%20to%20convene%20a%20special%20task%20force%20on%20nuclear%20energy%20within%20three%20months%20in%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20Indo-French%20Strategic%20Dialogue.%20On%20the%20issue%20of%20Small%20Modular%20Reactors%20(SMRs)%20the%20potential%20for%20cooperation%20exists%20as%20India%20needs%20to%20enhance%20the%20capacity%20of%20its%20own%20indigenous%20SMRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20expressed%20satisfaction%20with%20their%20close%20cooperation%20through%20their%20jointly%20launched%20International%20Solar%20Alliance%20to%20support%20third%20countries%20in%20their%20solar%20programmes.%20They%20welcomed%20the%20agreement%20to%20support%20creation%20of%20a%20Solar%20Academy%20in%20Senegal%20through%20joint%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20of%20Airbus%20in%20partnership%20with%20Tata%20Advanced%20System%20to%20begin%20the%20assembly%20of%20civilian%20helicopters%20(H125)%20in%20India.%20They%20will%20become%20the%20first%20private%20sector%20company%20to%20produce%20helicopters%20in%20India%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20strategy%20of%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat.%20Airbus%20is%20also%20placing%20growing%20orders%20for%20aircraft%20parts%20in%20India%20for%20its%20assembly%20plants%20in%20Europe.%20Airlines%20in%20India%20have%20placed%20huge%20orders%20for%20Airbus%20planes.%20That%20Airbus%20builds%20planes%20in%20India%20as%20the%20company%20has%20done%20in%20China%20is%20met%20with%20reservations%20by%20France%2C%20which%20has%20experienced%20China's%20technology%20theft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20meeting%20with%20select%20Indian%20business%20leaders%2C%20Macron%20pressed%20for%20Indian%20investments%20in%20France%20for%20which%20his%20government%20was%20considering%20legislation%20similar%20to%20the%20US%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act.%20Indian%20companies%20could%20invest%20in%20French%20advanced%20technology%20companies%20but%20without%20acquiring%20control.%20With%20the%20huge%20database%20in%20India%20and%20human%20talent%20available%20there%20was%20great%20scope%20of%20cooperation%20in%20AI.%20Macron%20was%20not%20fully%20aware%20of%20the%20huge%20investments%20being%20made%20in%20developing%20infrastructure%20in%20India%20and%20was%20keen%20that%20French%20companies%20participate%20in%20this%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron's%20late%20night%20visit%20to%20Dargah%20Nizamuddin%20Aulia%20before%20his%20departure%20from%20India%20was%20intended%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20constituencies%20back%20home%20about%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20in%20India.%20That%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20accompanied%20him%20was%20diplomatic%20on%20our%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kanwal%20Sibal%20was%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Ambassador%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Russia%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Of%20Mission%20in%20Washington.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706519400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3t2bipmo_pm-modi-and-macron_625x300_27_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-strong-political-message-behind-macrons-india-visit-4953013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Emmanuel%20Macron's%20visit%20to%20India%20as%20chief%20guest%20at%20our%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20had%20a%20ceremonial%20aspect%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20but%20in%20relations%20between%20states%20ceremonial%20gestures%20convey%20a%20message%20at%20many%20levels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-strong-political-message-behind-macrons-india-visit-4953013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-strong-political-message-behind-macrons-india-visit-4953013%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-strong-political-message-behind-macrons-india-visit-4953013%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20flagship%20stock%20may%20return%20over%2050%25%2C%20Cantor%20Fitzgerald%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706519096000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107227305%2Cimgsize-66198.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-busin