trong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-vs-bjp-over-hanuman-flag-removal-in-karnataka-more-protests-today-4951128%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECongress%20vs%20BJP%20As%20Hanuman%20Flag%20Removed%20In%20Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20protests%20this%20morning%20in%20Mandya%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20including%20Bengaluru%2C%20show%20dozens%20of%20men%20and%20women%2C%20brandishing%20Hanuman%20flags%20or%20wearing%20saffron%20scarves%2C%20clash%20with%20the%20police.%20One%20video%2C%20shared%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20showed%20police%20detaining%20BJP%20workers%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Karnataka%20Police%20detain%20BJP%20workers%20protesting%20in%20Bengaluru%20over%20the%20Mandya%20flag%20issue.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMandya%20district%20administration%20yesterday%20brought%20down%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20hoisted%20by%20the%20Gram%20Panchayat%20Board%20of%20Mandya%20district.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7RhJZvEjpK%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7RhJZvEjpK%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FIntYMOKKAA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FIntYMOKKAA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1751838976317808753%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20underlined%20continuing%20tension%20in%20the%20Keragodu%20village%20area%20-%20where%20orders%20banning%20large%20gathering%20have%20been%20in%20place%20since%20last%20evening%20-%20and%20a%20third%2C%20from%20when%20the%20flag%20was%20taken%20down%2C%20showed%20protesters%20and%20police%2C%20armed%20with%20lathis%2C%20facing-off%20over%20metal%20barricades%20that%20are%20overrun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20a%20large%20police%20contingent%20was%20positioned%20after%20people%20from%20the%20village%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20mob%20of%20BJP%2C%20JDS%2C%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20members%2C%20gathered%20to%20protest.%20Police%20resorted%20to%20a%20mild%20lathi%20charge%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhat%20Was%20The%20Hanuman%20Flag%20Incident%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Keragodu%20village%20residents%2C%20and%20those%20of%20a%20dozen%20others%20in%20the%20region%2C%20funded%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20flag%20near%20a%20temple.%20Reports%20indicated%20the%20BJP%20and%20JDS%20were%20also%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20flag%20post%20was%20completed%2C%20the%20villagers%20ran%20up%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%2C%20prompting%20protests%20from%20other%20individuals%20who%20complained%20to%20the%20district%20administration.%20Acting%20on%20these%20complaints%2C%20the%20taluk%20panchayat%20chief%20executive%20directed%20the%20gram%20panchayat%20officials%20to%20remove%20the%20flag%2C%20PTI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20Sri%20Gourishankar%20Seva%20Trust%20had%20been%20allowed%20to%20fly%20the%20national%20flag%2C%20and%20that%20hoisting%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20rules.%20The%20flag%20was%20pulled%20down%2C%20prompting%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Vice%20President%20of%20the%20village%20panchayat%20has%20said%20the%20letter%20requesting%20permission%20to%20hoist%20a%20flag%20referred%20specifically%20to%20its%20use%20for%20%26quot%3Breligious%20purposes%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20does%20not%20know%20the%20reality%20of%20this%20controversy...%20the%20district%20officer%20has%20given%20him%20wrong%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Virupaksha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20wrote%20the%20request%20letter%2C%20we%20mentioned%20would%20also%20use%20this%20for%20religious%20purposes.%20What%20we%20are%20requesting%20is%20to%20permit%20us%20to%20hoist%20the%20saffron%20flag%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20village%20leader%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EPolitical%20Row%20Over%20Hanuman%20Flag%20Removal%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hanuman%20flag%20row%20has%20led%2C%20predictably%2C%20to%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20JDS%2C%20fresh%20from%20an%20alliance%20before%20the%20general%20election%2C%20accusing%20the%20government%20of%20%26quot%3Bappeasement%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20begun%20a%20'%3Cem%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fem%3E'%20from%20Keragodu%20to%20the%20District%20Collector's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20his%20deputy%2C%20DK%20Shivakumar%2C%20have%20both%20played%20down%20their%20rivals'%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20it%20was%20incorrect%20to%20hoist%20the%20Hanuman%20flag%20when%20permission%20had%20not%20been%20instead%20of%20the%20national%20flag.%20This%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20them%20do%20politics%20(if%20they%20want)...%20but%20they%20should%20not%20take%20the%20law%20into%20their%20hands.%20We%20respect%20all%20religions...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20BJP%20workers%20are%20protesting%2C%20at%20district%20HQs%20across%20the%20state%2C%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-Hindu%20policy%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20whom%20they%20have%20accused%20of%20%26quot%3Binsulting%26quot%3B%20the%20national%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EImpact%20Of%20Hanuman%20Flag%20Removal%20Protests%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20in%20Keragodu%20village%20is%20at%20a%20standstill%3B%20police%20have%20erected%20barricades%20around%20the%20flagpole%20and%20CCTV%20cameras%20have%20been%20installed%20to%20ensure%20no%20untoward%20incidents%20occur%2C%20sources%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3