2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107227022.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrance-to-push-for-eu-law-changes-as-farmers-block-paris-highways%2Farticleshow%2F107227022.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrance-to-push-for-eu-law-changes-as-farmers-block-paris-highways%2Famp_articleshow%2F107227022.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrance-to-push-for-eu-law-changes-as-farmers-block-paris-highways%2Famp_articleshow%2F107227022.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Schirkoa%20-%20An%20Animation%20Film%20Of%20Stunning%20Power%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20bravura%20parable%20built%20around%20a%20range%20of%20zany%20ideas%20and%20marked%20by%20dazzling%20visual%20flair%20and%20precision%2C%20%3Cem%3ESchirkoa%20%E2%80%93%20In%20Lies%20We%20Trust%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20animation%20film%20of%20stunning%20power.%20It%20is%20as%20potent%20as%20cinema%20as%20it%20is%20pertinent%20as%20commentary.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20103-minute%20film%20combines%203D%20mo-cap%20and%202D%20techniques%20to%20achieve%20a%20magical%20meld%20of%20dystopian%20noir%20elements%2C%20flights%20of%20sci-fi%20fantasy%20and%20urgent%20contemporary%20concerns.%20The%20impeccably%20crafted%2C%20compelling%20film%20is%20punky%2C%20pulpy%20and%20profane.%20It%20is%20at%20the%20same%20time%20profound%2C%20political%20and%20philosophical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWritten%2C%20designed%20and%20directed%20by%20debutant%20Ishan%20Shukla%2C%20the%20film%2C%20based%20on%20his%20much-awarded%202016%20short%20fiction%3Cem%3E%20Schirkoa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20sustains%20the%20balance%20between%20conflicting%20impulses%20without%20missing%20a%20beat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESchirkoa%20%E2%80%93%20In%20Lies%20We%20Trust%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20had%20its%20world%20premiere%20at%20the%20International%20Film%20Festival%20Rotterdam%202024%20on%20Sunday%2C%20represents%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20for%20Indian%20animation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20from%20the%20excesses%20and%20limitations%20of%20the%20Bollywood%20idiom%20and%20the%20devices%20of%20mythological%20epics%2C%20it%20stylishly%20juggles%20many%20provocative%20notions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20finiteness%20of%20resistance%20as%20a%20fuel%20for%20art%2C%20the%20irrelevance%20of%20rebels%20in%20a%20perfect%20world%2C%20sex%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20thoughts%20of%20death%2C%20fear-mongering%20as%20a%20tool%20of%20oppression%20and%20much%20else%20-%20and%20sprinkles%20them%20across%20an%20over-arching%20tale%20of%20an%20oppressed%20people%20seeking%20deliverance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemarkably%20inventive%20and%20wide-ranging%20with%20its%20colour%20palette%2C%20its%20filming%20technique%20and%20its%20characters%2C%20%3Cem%3ESchirkoa%20%E2%80%93%20In%20Lies%20We%20Trust%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20not%20hinge%20on%20a%20cocksure%20male%20protagonist%20fighting%20for%20the%20vulnerable.%20The%20hero%20is%20hobbled%20by%20grave%20doubts%20as%20he%20looks%20for%20a%20way%20out%20of%20a%20world%20that%20deprives%20him%20of%20freedom%20of%20thought%20and%20action.%20He%20hurtles%20into%20situations%20and%20rarely%20so%20of%20his%20own%20volition.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20scales%20a%20creative%20high%20that%20no%20Indian%20animated%20feature%20has%20ever%20come%20within%20striking%20distance%20of.%20It%20yanks%20open%20a%20door%20and%20forays%20into%20a%20domain%20where%20art%2C%20imagination%20and%20innovation%20coalesce%20to%20perfection%20and%20yield%20a%20highly%20entertaining%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principal%20voice%20cast%20%E2%80%93%20Golshifteh%20Farahani%2C%20Asia%20Argento%2C%20Soko%2C%20King%20Khan%2C%20John%20Sutton%20and%20Denzil%20Smith%20%E2%80%93%20is%20to%20die%20for.%20It%20is%20supported%20by%20guest%20stars%20Lav%20Diaz%2C%20Karan%20Johar%2C%20Anurag%20Kashyap%2C%20Shekhar%20Kapur%2C%20Piyush%20Mishra%20and%20Gaspar%20Noe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESneha%20Khanwalkar's%20standout%20background%20score%20captures%20the%20ever-changing%20moods%20of%20a%20film%20that%20ranges%20from%20the%20sombre%20and%20melancholic%20to%20the%20riotous%20and%20rebellious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soundtrack%20is%20embellished%20with%20delightfully%20evocative%20songs%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20which%20are%20composed%20and%20performed%20by%20Khanwalkar%20(who%20also%20lends%20her%20voice%20to%20a%20tertiary%20character)%20with%20several%20others%20being%20contributed%20by%20King%20Khan%20and%20his%20band.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20level%2C%20%3Cem%3ESchirkoa%20%E2%80%93%20In%20Lies%20We%20Trust%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexplores%20the%20pitfalls%20of%20unquestioning%20faith%20in%20false%20gods%20and%20the%20hysterical%20conformity%20that%20it%20demands.%20It%20probes%20the%20nature%20of%20autocracy%20and%20the%20fight%20against%20indoctrination%20and%20the%20brutal%20enforcement%20of%20repressive%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20pans%20out%20in%20a%20society%20trapped%20in%20a%20system%20that%20dreads%20diversity.%20Citizens%20are%20ordained%20by%20law%20to%20wear%20paper%20bags%20over%20their%20heads%20to%20erase%20their%20differences.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20alike%20is%20the%20way%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20an%20axiom%20that%20is%20repeatedly%20drilled%20into%20them.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hero%2C%20197A%20(Shahbaz%20Sarwar%20and%20Tibu%20Fortes%2C%20the%20film's%20two%20debuting%20actors)%20%E2%80%93%20residents%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Schirkoa%20have%20no%20names%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20new%20council%20member%20in%20love%20with%20242B%20(Farahani)%2C%20who%20has%20an%20audacious%20plan.%20She%20hopes%20to%20escape%20the%20nightmare.%20She%20pleads%20with%20her%20boyfriend%20to%20join%20her.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20male%20protagonist%2C%20irresolute%20and%20tentative%2C%20decides%20to%20stay%20on%20and%20be%20co-opted.%20The%20decision%20sparks%20a%20chain%20of%20events%20that%20leads%20him%20into%20another%20realm%20and%20sharpens%20his%20awareness%20of%20the%20possibilities%20that%20lie%20yonder.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20lies%20beyond%20the%20overly%20regulated%20society%20that%20197A%20and%20his%20ilk%20inhabit%20moves%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20action%20as%20Schirkoa%2C%20on%20the%20back%20of%20its%20protagonist%2C%20travels%20into%20a%20new%20reality.%20The%20music%2C%20tone%20and%20texture%20of%20the%20film%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20hero's%20appearance%20and%20voice%2C%20undergo%20transformations%20as%20the%20backdrop%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20stokes%20fear%20of%20dangerous%20immigrants%20camping%20at%20the%20borders.%20A%20myth%20of%20a%20city%20of%20evil%20refugees%20is%20spread%20to%20keep%20Schirkoans%20in%20check.%20Repeated%20announcements%20(the%20voice%20of%20Karan%20Johar)%20remind%20the%20people%20of%20the%20need%20to%20abide%20by%20Schirkoa's%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20trio%20%E2%80%93%20Safety%2C%20Sanity%20and%20Sanctity%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insides%20of%20a%20bus%20that%20242B%20wants%20to%20board%20on%20her%20way%20out%20of%20Schirkoa%20is%20a%20colourful%20and%20chaotic%20world%20peopled%20by%20oddballs%20and%20rebels%2C%20a%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20dull%20hues%20that%20the%20browbeaten%20folks%20of%20Schirkoa%20sport.%20One%20of%20the%20bus%20passengers%20is%20an%20astrologer%20(Piyush%20Mishra)%20who%20makes%20predictions%20in%20flowery%20Hindi%20verse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20of%20Konthaqa%2C%20where%20a%20mermaid%20named%20Lies%20(Asia%20Argento)%20runs%20the%20show%20and%20a%20wacky%20impresario%2C%20Mord%20(King%20Khan)%2C%20assembles%20performers%20for%20a%20musical%20contest%2C%20is%20no%20less%20rambunctious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20that%20the%20Schirkoans%20%E2%80%93%20presented%20largely%20as%20a%20nebulous%20entity%20in%20perpetually%20aimless%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20are%20wholly%20unaware%20of%20what%20lies%20beyond%20the%20boundaries%20of%20their%20city%20and%20what%20lies%20are%20being%20perpetuated%20to%20keep%20them%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgitated%20students%20hold%20demonstrations%2C%20street%20protests%20erupt%2C%20a%20mysterious%20girl%20(Soko)%20prowls%20in%20the%20shadows%2C%20and%20the%20city's%20safety%20personnel%20swing%20into%20action%20with%20their%20guns%20and%20batons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rumours%20about%20a%20mythical%20land%20of%20the%20free%20inhabited%20by%20people%20referred%20to%20as%20Anomalies%20are%20circulated%20by%20the%20ruling%20clique%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20extracting%20political%20gains%2C%20but%20as%20the%20whisper%20campaign%20reaches%20a%20crescendo%2C%20the%20ploy%20backfires%20and%20the%20air%20is%20filled%20with%20talk%20of%20rebellion.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entertaining%2C%20edgy%20allegory%20about%20power%2C%20suppression%20of%20dissent%20and%20the%20people's%20yearning%20for%20personal%20freedom%20pulsates%20with%20energy.%20The%20film%2C%20transports%20the%20audience%20into%20a%20fantastical%20universe%20where%20burning%20issues%20need%20urgent%20attention%20and%20provoke%20simmering%20discontent.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESchirkoa%20%E2%80%93%20In%20Lies%20We%20Trust%3C%2Fem%3E%20draws%20its%20power%20primarily%20from%20a%20storyline%20that%20springs%20many%20a%20surprise%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20technology%20and%20the%20use%20it%20puts%20it%20to.%20It%20is%20shot%20in%20a%20video%20game%20engine%20that%20enables%20it%20to%20acquire%20depth%20of%20vision%2C%20solidity%20of%20structure%20and%20steady%20control%20over%20the%20design%20elements.%20Shukla's%20grasp%20on%20the%20medium%20is%20phenomenal.%20Add%20to%20that%20the%20fertile%20imagination%20that%20permeates%20the%20film%20and%20you%20have%20a%20work%20of%20pure%2C%20staggering%20cinematic%20spunk.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706518020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fqoh3q0io_alia-_625x300_29_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fschirkoa-in-lies-we-trust-review-an-animation-film-of-stunning-power-4952903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Schirkoa%20In%20Lies%20We%20Trust%20Review%3A%20The%20film%20scales%20a%20creative%20high%20that%20no%20Indian%20animated%20feature%20has%20ever%20come%20within%20striking%20distance%20of.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fschirkoa-in-lies-we-trust-review-an-animation-film-of-stunning-power-4952903%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biometrics-based%20immigration%20checks%20at%20these%20airports%20soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706517960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107226723%2Cimgsize-84672.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fbiometrics-based-immigration-checks-at-new-delhi-mumbai-bengaluru-airports-soon-digiyatra-e-passports%2Farticleshow%2F107224653.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Biometrics-based%20immigration%20checks%20at%20Indian%20airports%20soon!%20The%20Indian%20government%20is%20set%20to%20implement%20a%20faster%20biometrics-based%20process%20for%20international%20passengers%20to%20expedite%20immigration%20checks.%20The%20airports%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20will%20introduce%20automated%20immigration%20clearances%2C%20allowing%20international%20entries%20and%20departures%20without%20physical%20passport%20verification.%20The%20DigiYatra%20app%2C%20currently%20used%20by%20domestic%20passengers%2C%2