20Parsis%20and%20Christians%2C%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%20who%20entered%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CAA%20will%20be%20implemented%20very%20soon.%20It%20will%20be%20implemented%20within%20seven%20days.%20This%20is%20my%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Thakur%2C%20also%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Matua%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%2C%20the%20union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20ports%2C%20shipping%20and%20waterways%2C%20has%20made%20a%20similar%20comment%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20claiming%20that%20the%20CAA%20would%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20country%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatuas%2C%20who%20constitute%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20state's%20Scheduled%20Caste%20population%2C%20had%20been%20migrating%20to%20West%20Bengal%20since%20the%201950s%2C%20primarily%20due%20to%20religious%20persecution%20in%20erstwhile%20East%20Pakistan%20which%20later%20became%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20nineties%2C%20political%20parties%20in%20West%20Bengal%20have%20actively%20sought%20to%20secure%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Matuas%2C%20who%2C%20due%20to%20their%20significant%20population%20and%20tendency%20to%20vote%20together%2C%20are%20considered%20a%20valuable%20voting%20bloc%20akin%20to%20the%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Matua%20community%20is%20believed%20to%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur's%20assertion%20on%20the%20CAA's%20implementation%20comes%20amidst%20reports%20this%20month%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20legislation%20would%20be%20notified%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20before%26quot%3B%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20elicited%20strong%20reactions%20from%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20in%20the%20state%2C%20whic