3BParents%20Shouldn't%20Treat%20Child's%20Report%20Card%20As%20Visiting%20Card%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20said%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20instill%20resilience%20in%20children%20to%20help%20them%20cope%20with%20pressures%20and%20asserted%20that%20parents%20and%20teachers%20should%20collectively%20address%20challenges%20faced%20by%20students.%20Interacting%20with%20students%2C%20parents%20and%20teachers%20during%20his%20annual%20Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%20programme%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20advised%20parents%20against%20treating%20their%20child's%20report%20card%20as%20their%20own%20visiting%20card%20and%20suggested%20that%20students%20should%20compete%20with%20themselves%20and%20not%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20crucial%20to%20instill%20resilience%20in%20our%20children%20and%20help%20them%20cope%20with%20pressures...%20We%20cannot%20do%20switch%20off%2C%20pressure%20is%20gone.%20One%20must%20become%20capable%20of%20bearing%20any%20kind%20of%20pressure.%20They%20should%20believe%20that%20pressure%20keeps%20on%20building%2C%20and%20one%20has%20to%20prepare%20oneself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20suggested%20students%20to%20%26quot%3Balways%20make%20friends%20who%20are%20more%20intelligent%20and%20work%20harder%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BYou%20must%20be%20inspired%20by%20such%20friends.%20Don't%20let%20the%20pressure%20of%20studies%20and%20examinations%20overpower%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20even%20though%20competition%20and%20challenges%20act%20as%20inspirations%20but%20competition%20must%20be%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLot%20of%20parents%20keep%20on%20giving%20examples%20of%20other%20children%20to%20their%20children.%20Parents%20should%20avoid%20doing%20these%20things...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20seen%20that%20those%20parents%20who%20have%20not%20been%20very%20successful%20in%20their%20lives%20have%20nothing%20to%20say%20or%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20world%20about%20their%20successes%20and%20achievements%2C%20make%20the%20report%20card%20of%20their%20children%20as%20their%20visiting%20card.%20Whenever%20they%20meet%20someone%2C%20they%20will%20tell%20them%20the%20story%20of%20their%20children.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BYou%20must%20not%20compare%20one%20child%20with%20another%20as%20that%20can%20be%20detrimental%20to%20their%20future.%20Some%20parents%20treat%20their%20children's%20report%20card%20as%20their%20visiting%20card%2C%20this%20is%20not%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20seventh%20episode%20of%20his%20outreach%20programme%20with%20students%20ahead%20of%20examinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20explained%20that%20the%20stress%20faced%20by%20students%20is%20of%20three%20types%20--induced%20by%20peer%20pressure%2C%20by%20parents%20and%20self%20induced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20times%2C%20children%20take%20pressure%20on%20themselves%20that%20they%20are%20not%20performing%20up%20to%20the%20mark.%20I%20suggest%20that%20you%20should%20set%20small%20goals%20during%20preparation%20and%20gradually%20improve%20your%20performance%2C%20this%20way%20you%20will%20be%20completely%20ready%20before%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20make%20ourselves%20capable%20of%20facing%20any%20sort%20of%20pressure.%20Students%20need%20to%20make%20themselves%20ready%20to%20go%20through%20any%20condition.%20If%20we%20visit%20any%20cold%20place%2C%20we%20make%20up%20our%20minds%2C%20and%20accordingly%2C%20we%20keep%20ourselves%20ready...(in%20the)%20same%20way%20you%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20challenges%20of%20students%20must%20be%20addressed%20collectively%20by%20parents%20and%20teachers.%20He%20also%20encouraged%20teachers%20to%20forge%20strong%20connections%20with%20their%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bond%20between%20educators%20and%20learners%20is%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20bright%20future.%20If%20teachers%20start%20working%20on%20building%20a%20relationship%20with%20their%20students%20from%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20year%2C%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20question%20of%20tension%20building%20up%20among%20students%20at%20the%20time%20of%20examinations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTeachers%20must%20expand%20their%20connections%20with%20students%20much%20beyond%20their%20subject%20syllabus%20so%20that%20students%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20their%20teachers%20even%20for%20the%20smallest%20of%20problems.%20Music%20teachers%20can%20not%20only%20help%20their%20own%20students%20deal%20with%20tensions%2C%20they%20can%20do%20so%20for%20students%20of%20the%20entire%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20questions%20on%20balancing%20studies%20with%20a%20healthy%20life%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20many%20students%20use%20mobile-phones%20and%20some%20do%20it%20for%20many%20hours.%20He%20advised%20students%20not%20to%20use%20their%20sleep%20time%20for%20watching%20reels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20understand%20that%20even%20mobiles%20need%20recharge%20to%20be%20used%2C%20and%20similarly%2C%20our%20body%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20recharged.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20students%20keep%20playing%20all%20the%20time%2C%20but%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20strike%20a%20balance.%20A%20healthy%20body%20is%20necessary%20for%20a%20healthy%20mind.%20Good%20and%20sound%20sleep%20is%20also%20a%20must%20for%20good%20health.%20Don't%20use%20your%20sleep%20time%20for%20watching%20reels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20into%20deep%20sleep%20within%2030%20seconds%20of%20lying%20on%20the%20bed%20on%20all%20365%20days.%20When%20I%20am%20awake%2C%20I%20am%20fully%20awake%2C%20but%20I%20am%20totally%20asleep%20while%20sleeping.%20Nutrition%20is%20also%20necessary.%20Our%20body%20must%20get%20the%20required%20nutrition.%20A%20good%20balance%20of%20food%20and%20regular%20exercise%20for%20fitness%20are%20also%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20also%20advised%20students%20to%20practice%20writing.%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20age%20of%20mobile%20phones%20and%20laptops%2C%20students%20are%20losing%20the%20practice%20to%20write%20while%20exams%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20handwritten.%20Of%20the%20time%20dedicated%20to%20studies%2C%20you%20should%20devote%20at%20least%2050%20per%20cent%20time%20to%20practise%20writing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20students%20as%20the%20shapers%20of%20India's%20future%2C%20Modi%20said%20the%20Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%20programme%20is%20like%20an%20examination%20for%20him%20too.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20students%20have%20become%20more%20innovative%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganised%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%20has%20been%20engaging%20students%2C%20parents%20and%20teachers%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20event%20has%20been%20held%20in%20a%20town%20hall%20format%20at%20the%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20here.%20An%20estimated%202.26%20crore%20registrations%20have%20taken%20place%20on%20the%20MyGov%20portal%2C%20highlighting%20the%20widespread%20enthusiasm%20among%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20fourth%20edition%20was%20held%20online%2C%20while%20the%20fifth%20and%20sixth%20editions%20returned%20to%20the%20town-hall%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706515920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fohu22s58_pm-modi-ndtv-650_650x400_29_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpariksha-pe-charcha-parents-shouldnt-treat-childs-report-card-as-visiting-card-pm-modi-4952658%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Monday%20said%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20instill%20resilience%20in%20children%20to%20help%20them%20cope%20with%20pressures%20and%20asserted%20that%20parents%20and%20teachers%20should%20collectively%20address%20challenges%20faced%20by%20students.%20Interacting%20with%20students%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpariksha-pe-charcha-parents-shouldnt-treat-childs-report-card-as-visiting-card-pm-modi-4952658%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpariksha-pe-charcha-parents-shouldnt-treat-childs-report-card-as-visiting-card-pm-modi-4952658%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpariksha-pe-charcha-parents-shouldnt-treat-childs-report-card-as-visiting-card-pm-modi-4952658%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maharashtra%3A%20Ministers%20Dissatisfied%20With%20Shinde%20Govt's%20Handling%20of%20Maratha%20Stir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F04170749%2FChhagan-Bhujbal.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Two%20Maharashtra%20politicians%20with%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20dispensation%20have%20expressed%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20are%20Union%20minister%20Narayan%20Rane%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20leader%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%2C%20who%20is%20also%20minister%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20cabinet.%20Both%20have%20opposed%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20extend%20benefits%20accorded%20to%20OBCs%20to%20Marathas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20Bhujbal%20especially%20noted%20that%20this%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbackdoor%20entry%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20community%20into%20the%20OBC%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhujbal%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20which%20aligned%20with%20the%20ruling%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20party%20and%20the%20BJP%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20stir%20has%20led%20to%20anxieties%20among%20existing%20OBC%20community%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20OBCs%20are%20having%20a%20feeling%20that%20they%20have%20lost%20their%20reservations%20as%20Marathas%20will%20take%20the%20benefits.%20I%20support%20giving%20a%20separate%20reservation%20to%20Marathas%2C%20but%20not%20sharing%20the%20existing%20OBC%20quota%20with%20them.%20Because%20once%20they%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20existing%20reservations%20for%20OBCs%2C%20only%20they%20will%20get%20the%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EMidday%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mid-day.com%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-news%2Farticle%2Fbhujbals-critique-of-govt-not-official-stand-of-ncp-23332285%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar%20division)%20leader%20Praful%20Patel%20has%20said%20that%20Bhujbal%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%C2%A0%20is%20not%20the%20official%20stand%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20said%20Bhujbal%E2%80%99s%20stand%20was%20that%20of%20the%20Samata%20Parishad%2C%20the%20OBC%20group%20headed%20by%20him%2C%20and%20not%20of%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhujbal%20said%20that%20retired%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Shinde%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20committee%20that%20will%20look%20into%20the%20Kunbi%20records%20of%20Marathas%2C%20receives%20an%20excessively%20high%20salary.%C2%A0He%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20gets%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%202.80%20lakh%2C%20Justice%20Shinde%20and%20the%20committee%20members%20get%20Rs%204.50%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706515344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F04170749%2FChhagan-Bhujbal.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchhagan-bhujbal-obc-narayan-rane-maratha-quota%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20minister%20Narayan%20Rane%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20leader%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%2C%20who%20is%20also%20minister%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20cabinet%2C%20have%20questioned%20the%20move.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchhagan-bhujbal-obc-narayan-rane-maratha-quota%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BVirat%20Spat%20At%20Me%2C%20I%20Said%20If%20You%20Do...%26quot%3B%3A%20SA%20Great's%20Stunning%20Revelation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20South%20Africa%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dean%20Elgar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1377-dean-elgar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDean%20Elgar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20international%20cricket%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20has%20made%20a%20shocking%20revelation%20from%20the%20Proteas'%20tour%20of%20India%20in%202015.%20Elgar%20claimed%20that%20former%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bspat%26quot%3B%20at%20him%20during%20the%20first%20Test%20of%20a%20four-match%20series%20at%20the%20IS%20Bindra%20Stadium%20in%20Mohali.%20Notably%2C%20the%20series%20against%20South%20Africa%20was%20Kohli's%20first%20at%20home%20as%20captain.%20Elgar%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20threatened%20to%20hit%20Kohli%20had%20he%20done%20the%20same%20thing%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20wickets%20were%20jokes.%20Like%20playing%20on%20that...%20that%20surface%20there.%20And%20I%20came%20into%20bat%20and%20I%20was%20actually%20like%20holding%20my%20own%20against%20Ashwin%20and%20what's%20his%20name%20Jeja%2C%20Jeja%2C%20Jeja%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E)%20(smiles)%20and%20Kohli%2C%20he%20like%20spat%20at%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Elgar%20said%20on%20%26quot%3BBanter%2C%20with%20The%20Boys%26quot%3B%20podcast%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5KT9WyBhpwU%5C%22%3EBetway%20South%20Africa%3C%2Fa%3E's%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%20to%20him%20if%20you%20do%20that%2C%20I'll%20f*****g%20*****%20you%20with%20this%20bat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20using%20a%20local%20profanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20Kohli%20knew%20the%20meaning%20of%20the%20word%2C%20Elgar%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20he%20did%20because%20de%20Villiers%20was%20his%20teammate%20at%20RCB%2C%20so%20he%20understood.%20And%20I%20said%20if%20you%20do%20that%2C%20I'll%20...%20on%20this%20field%2C%20I'll%20absolutely%20knock%20you%20out.%20And%20then%20%5Bhe%20said%5D%20'Hey%20F***%20you%2C%20F***%20you'%20(mimicking%20the%20Indian)%20but%20barking%20up%20the%20wrong%20tree%20yeah.%20Anyways%2C%20we%20are%20in%20India%20so%20you%20got%20to%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20cautious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElgar%2C%20however%2C%20revealed%20that%20Kohli%20apologised%20to%20him%20for%20his%20behaviour%20over%20a%20few%20drinks%20when%20India%20toured%20South%20Africa%20in%202017-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20three%20years%20later%2C%20Kohli%20pulled%20me%20aside%20and%20said%20'listen%2C%20can%20we%20go%20and%20have%20a%20drink%20after%20the%20series%20i%20want%20to%20apologise%20for%20my%20actions'.%20So%20we%20drank%20till%203%20in%20the%20morning.%20This%20is%20when%20he%20used%20to%20drink%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElgar%20played%20his%20last%20Test%20against%20India%20earlier%20this%20month%20at%20the%20Newlands%20in%20Cape%20Town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20final%20Test%2C%20Elgar%20captained%20South%20Africa%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Temba%20Bavuma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1540-temba-bavuma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETemba%20Bavuma%3C%2Fa%3E%20missing%20out%20due%20to%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20won%20the%20second%20Test%20to%20level%20the%20series%201-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706515140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3valpigo_dean-elgar-virat-kohli_625x300_29_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-spat-at-me-i-said-south-africa-greats-revelation-on-duel-with-india-star-4951829%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20South%20Africa%20captain%2C%20however%2C%20revealed%20that%20Virat%20Kohli%20apologised%20to%20him%20for%20his%20behavious%20over%20a%20few%20drinks%20when%20India%20toured%20South%20Africa%20in%202017-18.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20PM%20Modi%20Said%20During%20'Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha'%20With%20Students%3A%20Top%20Quotes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20to%20students%20today%20during%20'Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha'%20to%20motivate%20them%20ahead%20of%20the%20board%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20competition%20and%20challenges%20act%20as