orale%20and%20confidence%20through%20comparisons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20advised%20parents%20against%20treating%20their%20child's%20report%20card%20as%20their%20own%20visiting%20card.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706515020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fc36fcq2o_narendra-modi_625x300_29_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pm-narendra-modi-told-students-and-parents-during-pariksha-pe-charcha-4952553%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20spoke%20to%20students%20today%20during%20'Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha'%20to%20motivate%20them%20ahead%20of%20the%20board%20exams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pm-narendra-modi-told-students-and-parents-during-pariksha-pe-charcha-4952553%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pm-narendra-modi-told-students-and-parents-during-pariksha-pe-charcha-4952553%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pm-narendra-modi-told-students-and-parents-during-pariksha-pe-charcha-4952553%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Expats%3A%20Nicole%20Kidman%20show%20about%20Hong%20Kong%20not%20shown%20in%20city%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706514859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2902%2Fproduction%2F_132489401_gettyimages-1234832184.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68125715%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20a%20show%20about%20the%20life%20of%20foreigners%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20-%20but%20has%20aired%20everywhere%20except%20the%20city%20itself.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A74%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68125715%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68125715.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-68125715.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CNN%20Philippines%20to%20Close%20Down%2C%20With%20300%20Jobs%20Losses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706514545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F10%2Fcnn_philippines.jpg%3Fcrop%3D116px%252C278px%252C1600px%252C891px%26resize%3D1000%252C563%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235890177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CNN%20Philippines%20is%20to%20close%20down%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20on%20Monday%20local%20time.%20The%20move%20means%20up%20to%20300%20jobs%20will%20be%20lost.%20CNN%20Philippines%20was%20launched%20in%202015%20under%20a%20brand%20licensing%20agreement%20between%20Turner%20and%20Nine%20Media%20Network%2C%20a%20Philippines%20company%20that%20is%20a%20wholly-owned%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20ALC%20Group%20of%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Patrick%20Frater%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fcnn-philippines-close-down-1235890177%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fcnn-philippines-close-down-1235890177%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fcnn-philippines-close-down-1235890177%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Karpoori's%20Formula%2C%20Modi's%20Alchemy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20her%20caste%20regulations%20India%20recognized%20differences%2C%20but%20not%20the%20mutability%20which%20is%20the%20law%20of%20life...%20Life%20departed%20from%20her%20social%20system%20and%20in%20its%20place%20she%20is%20worshipping%20with%20all%20ceremony%20the%20magnificent%20cage%20of%20countless%20compartments%20that%20she%20has%20manufactured.%20-%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%20Nationalism.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20Ratna%20is%20the%20rare%20honour%20that%20India's%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20complete%20discretion%20over.%20There%20is%20no%20formal%20recommendation%20necessary%20and%20it%20does%20not%20seek%20any%20qualification.%20The%20PM%20recommends%20the%20name%20of%20the%20person%20to%20the%20President%20who%20recognizes%20them%20as%20a%20jewel%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20India%2C%20the%20highest%20honour%20the%20country%20can%20bestow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20chose%20to%20award%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%202024%20to%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20Karpoori%20Thakur.%20The%20socialist%20icon%20is%20credited%20with%20introducing%20reservation%20in%20state%20jobs%20for%20backward%20castes.%20Now%20famous%20as%20the%20'Karpoori%20Thakur%20formula'%2C%20the%20cascading%20quota%20system%20had%20an%20overall%2026%25%20cap.%20Other%20backward%20communities%20got%2012%25%20of%20it%20and%20the%20economically%20backward%20classes%20among%20them%20could%20claim%20another%208%25.%20Crucially%2C%20women%20and%20the%20poor%20got%203%25%20each%2C%20which%20served%20the%20upper%20castes%20well.%20Therein%20also%20lies%20a%20tale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20lawyer-politician%2C%20Shanti%20Bhushan%2C%20writes%20in%20his%20autobiography%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3ECourting%20Destiny%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20how%20the%20formula%20was%20devised.%20Chief%20minister%20Thakur%20announced%20the%2026%25%20quota%20in%201978%20without%20even%20consulting%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues.%20That%20led%20Janata%20Party%20president%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20to%20set%20up%20a%20panel%20with%20Thakur%20and%20some%20ministers%20as%20members%20to%20sort%20out%20the%20issue.%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20union%20law%20minister%20in%20the%20Morarji%20Desai%20government%2C%20was%20made%20convenor%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhushan%20told%20Thakur%20he%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20alienate%20the%20powerful%20upper%20castes.%20To%20which%20Thakur%20said%20he%20could%20not%20help%20it%20because%20constitutionally%20upper%20castes%20could%20not%20have%20quotas.%20Bhushan%20suggested%20two%203%25%20carve-outs%20based%20on%20gender%20and%20income%2C%20irrespective%20of%20caste.%20He%20reasoned%20that%20upper%20caste%20women%20being%20better%20educated%20and%20socially%20mobile%20will%20corner%20almost%20the%20entire%20quota.%20All%20other%20criteria%20remaining%20equal%2C%20the%20low-income%20category%20would%20also%20become%20a%20default%20quota%20for%20poor%20social%20elites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20formula%20would%20be%20well%20within%20the%20Constitution%20and%20assuage%20upper%20castes%20somewhat%20as%20they%20would%20enjoy%206%25%20reservation.%20Bhushan%20suggested%20a%20further%20split%20of%20the%20remaining%2020%25%20between%20most%20backward%20and%20less%20backward%20castes.%20This%20was%20a%20bulwark%20against%20relatively%20upwardly%20mobile%20communities%20such%20as%20Yadavs%20and%20Kurmis%20cornering%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20quota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20background%20of%20elite%20inclusion%20makes%20Thakur's%20choice%20for%20Bharat%20Ratna%20an%20interesting%20one%20for%20its%20timing.%20The%20government%20could%20have%20honoured%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%2C%20the%20doyen%20of%20socialist%20politics%20in%20India%20and%20once%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20predecessor%2C%20the%20Jan%20Sangh.%20Lohia%20was%20the%20principal%20architect%20of%20the%20first%20opposition%20alliance%20to%20successfully%20challenge%20the%20Congress%20Party's%20dominance%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar.%20His%20nudge%20helped%20Thakur%20become%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20Jan-Sangh%20supported%20Bihar%20government%2C%20which%20eventually%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20creative%20quota%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnti-Congressism%20was%20Dr%20Lohia's%20heart%20and%20soul%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Fremembering-dr-lohia-544176%5C%22%3Epaying%20tribute%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Lohia%20on%20his%20birth%20anniversary%20in%20March%202019.%20%26quot%3BThose%20parties%20that%20claim%20inspiration%20from%20Dr%20Lohia%20have%20completely%20abandoned%20his%20principles...today%20those%20parties%20that%20falsely%20claim%20to%20be%20Dr%20Lohia's%20followers%20are%20desperate%20to%20form%20an%20opportunistic%20%3Cem%3EMaha%20Milawat%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20adulteration%20alliances%20with%20the%20same%20Congress.%20It%20is%20both%20ironical%20and%20reprehensible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20weeks%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20were%20to%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20PM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Fa-tribute-to-jan-nayak-karpoori-thakur-ji-578509%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Karpoori%20Thakur's%20anti-Congressism%20and%20reservation%20policies.%20%26quot%3BUnder%20his%20leadership%2C%20policies%20were%20implemented%20that%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20society%2C%20where%20one's%20birth%20did%20not%20determine%20one's%20fate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20viral%20op-ed.%20%26quot%3BHe%20belonged%20to%20the%20most%20backward%20strata%20of%20society%20but%20he%20worked%20for%20all%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%20He%20went%20on%20to%20recall%20that%20he%20himself%20belonged%20to%20a%20backward%20community%20but%20like%20Thakur%2C%20worked%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaste%20has%20always%20been%20a%20key%20variable%20in%20all%20Indian%20elections%20but%20plays%20a%20central%20role%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat's%20remark%20to%20have%20a%20relook%20at%20the%20quota%20system%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20cost%20the%20BJP%20the%202015%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20Bharat%20Ratna%20award%20has%20already%20set%20the%20cat%20among%20the%20pigeons%20in%20Bihar%20with%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20leader%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20chief%20minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leader%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20mentored%20by%20Thakur%2C%20claiming%20to%20be%20his%20true%20legatees.%20While%20Kumar%20set%20off%20the%20current%20wave%20of%20competitive%20caste%20politics%20with%20the%20Bihar%20Caste%20Census%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20has%20tried%20to%20keep%20up%2C%20demanding%20a%20national%20caste%20census%20for%20%3Cem%3Ejitni%20aabadi%2C%20utna%20haq%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rights%20according%20to%20population).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20Modi%20may%20have%20wrested%20the%20initiative%20away%20from%20the%20Lohiaites%20while%20also%20signalling%20to%20upper%20caste%20voters%20that%20there%20may%20be%20creative%20ways%20to%20address%20their%20worries%20should%20they%20stay%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20spectacular%20display%20of%20ruthless%20opportunism%2C%20chief%20minister%20and%20non-Yadav%20claimant%20of%20Thakur's%20legacy%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20has%20dumped%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20to%20return%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20writer%20is%20editor%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdaily.thesignal.co%5C%22%3EThe%20Signal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20author%20of%20The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706514360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fecklqdv8_karpoori-thakur_625x300_24_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fkarpooris-formula-modis-alchemy-4952548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20background%20of%20elite%20inclusion%20makes%20Thakur's%2