0834%2F%5C%22%3Ewould%20not%20recognise%20this%20suspension%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20this%20stubborn%20insistence%2C%20the%20suspended%20WFI%20has%20organised%20a%20%E2%80%98senior%20nationals%E2%80%99%20meet%20in%20Pune%20between%20January%2029%20and%2031.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Fat-suspended-wfi-nationals-wrestlers-in-fix-venue-infested-by-mosquitoes-9131985%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20the%20venue%20is%20infested%20with%20mosquitoes%20and%20most%20top%20names%20across%20weight%20categories%20have%20not%20made%20an%20appearance.%20%E2%80%9CMaharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Atish%20Todkar%2C%20who%20beat%20Ravi%20Dahiya%20in%20the%20Asian%20Games%20trials%20in%20July%202023%2C%20is%20the%20only%20notable%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20aren%E2%80%99t%20any%20big%20names%20in%20the%20fray%20here%20as%20Railways%20and%20Services%20aren%E2%80%99t%20coming%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20at%20the%20event%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaction%20from%20within%20the%2024%20state%20bodies%20have%20tried%20to%20send%20in%20a%20collection%20of%20wrestlers%20in%20an%20attempted%20show%20of%20strength%20in%20support%20of%20Sanjay%20Singh.%20But%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20states%2C%20barring%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20are%20also%20sending%20a%20full%20team%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20where%20the%20medal%20winners%20will%20proceed%20to%20a%20national%20camp%20and%20be%20considered%20for%20trials%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20situation%20%E2%80%93%20with%20two%20competing%20tournaments%20within%20a%20week%20of%20each%20other%20%E2%80%93%20has%20left%20wrestlers%20in%20a%20conundrum%2C%20as%20it%20is%20unclear%20which%20one%20will%20lead%20the%20way%20forward.%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%2072%20kg%20