x%20court%E2%80%99s%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20given%20our%20approval%20of%20Rs%20800%20crores%20%5Bin%20the%20latest%20tranche%5D%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20building.%20Now%20just%20hope%20that%20no%20one%20comes%20with%20a%20petition%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20useless%20spending%20like%20what%20happened%20during%20the%20Central%20Vista%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2F800-crores-approved-new-supreme-court-building-prime-minister-narendra-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Bar%20and%20Bench.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20added%20that%20since%202014%2C%20when%20he%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20allocated%20over%20Rs%207%2C000%20crore%20for%20the%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20said%20that%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Ram%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Csource%20of%20inspiration%20for%20the%20constitution%20makers%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20He%20said%20pictures%20of%20Ram%2C%20Sita%20and%20Lakshman%20%E2%80%93%20who%20feature%20in%20the%20epic%20%3Cem%3ERamayan%3C%2Fem%3E%20adorned%20the%20pages%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20was%20constructed%20after%20a%202019%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Hindu%20litigants%20in%20the%20dispute%20over%20the%20title.%20The%20temple%20stands%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20%E2%80%93%20demolished%20by%20kar%20sevaks%20in%201992%20%E2%80%93%20once%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-addresses-75th-anniversary-celebrations-of-the-supreme-court-in-new-delhi%2Farticle67785757.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20that%20Modi%20also%20complimented%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20for%20his%20efforts%20to%20improve%20ease%20of%20justice%20in%20the%20country.%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20bench%20that%20delivered%20the%20aforementioned%202019%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20also%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20using%20technology%20for%20ease%20of%20justice%2C%20which%20he%20also%20stressed%20as%20the%20right%20of%20every%20Indian%20citizen.%20He%20called%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20its%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECJI%20Chandrachud%20chaired%20the%20ceremonial%20bench%20with%20all%20apex%20court%20judges%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justices%20of%2025%20high%20courts%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findependence-of-judiciary-depends-on-the-freedom-of-every-individual-judge-to-decide-without-pressure-or-bias-cji%2Farticle67786330.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20noted%20that%20he%20said%20that%20an%20independent%20judiciary%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cmerely%20mean%20the%20insulation%20of%20the%20institution%20from%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20legislature%20branches%20but%20also%20the%20independence%20of%20individual%20judges%20in%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20roles%20as%20judges.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20art%20of%20judging%20must%20be%20free%20of%20social%20and%20political%20pressure%20and%20from%20the%20inherent%20biases%20which%20human%20beings%20hold%2C%E2%80%9D%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20efforts%20had%20been%20undertaken%20to%20train%20judges%20to%20%E2%80%9Cunlearn%20their%20subconscious%20attitudes%20inculcated%20by%20social%20conditioning%20on%20gender%2C%20disability%2C%20race%2C%20caste%20and%20sexuality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20has%20been%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkaran-thapar-justice-ch