0China%2C%20says%20retired%20US%20Navy%20Adm.%20James%20Stavridis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20has%20the%20world's%20largest%20navy%2C%20with%20over%20355%20vessels%20in%20its%20fleet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20experience%2C%20but%20quantity%20has%20a%20quality%20on%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Stavridis%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20going%20to%20have%20to%20expand%20its%20Navy%20and%20get%20more%20boats%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20China's%20forces%2C%20says%20retired%20US%20Navy%20Adm.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-firm-carlyle-hires-nato-commander-to-train-partners-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJames%20Stavridis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20Nobel%20Prize-winning%20mathematician%20to%20realize%20the%20number%20of%20Chinese%20ships%20is%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20outpace%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Stavridis%2C%20a%20%3Cspan%3Eformer%20NATO%20commander%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Esaid%20in%20a%20Sunday%20radio%20interview%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwabcradio.com%2Fshow%2Fthe-cats-roundtable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Cats%20Roundtable%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20leaked%20US%20Navy%20intelligence%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-chinas-shipbuilding-capacity-200-times-greater-than-us-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina's%20shipbuilding%20capacity%20is%20232%20times%20greater%20than%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-navy-destroyers-photos-fleet-list-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld's%20largest%20navy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20over%20355%20vessels%20in%20its%20fleet%2C%20per%20a%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.usni.org%2F2021%2F11%2F03%2Fchina-has-worlds-largest-navy-with-355-ships-and-counting-says-pentagon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Navy%20Institute%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20US%20has%20a%20smaller%20fleet%20of%20296%20ships%2C%20according%20to%20a%202021%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fanalysis%2Fus-military-forces-fy-2022-navy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenter%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20lot%20more%20experience%2C%20but%20quantity%20has%20a%20quality%20on%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20Stavridis%20told%20radio%20host%20John%20Catsimatidis.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20build%20more%20warships.%20We%20need%20to%20think%20about%20a%20US%20Navy%20that%20approaches%20350%20ships.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20policemen%2C%20but%20we%20want%20to%20live%20in%20a%20safe%20neighborhood.%20And%20sometimes%20that%20means%20having%20very%20capable%20military%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Stavridis%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20a%20bigger%20Navy%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Stavridis%20has%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20US%20and%20China's%20naval%20capabilities%2C%20and%20how%20they%20stack%20up%20against%20each%20other.%20Stavridis%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmichaelmedved.com%2Fhighlight%2Fadmiral-stavridis-on-the-medved-show%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Michael%20Medved%20Show%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-not-ready-war-us-10-years-ex-nato-chief-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20isn't%20ready%20to%20take%20on%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20China%20is%20building%20a%20massive%20fleet%2C%20even%20though%20they're%20acting%20very%20aggressively%2C%20they're%20not%20ready%20yet%20to%20line%20up%20all%20that