%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Stavridis%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-nato-chief-war-ukraine-end-just-like-korean-war-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706501108000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b7116843bb77284ba134d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-nato-chief-war-ukraine-end-just-like-korean-war-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRussia%20will%20probably%20still%20have%20control%20of%20some%20portion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20Crimea%2C%20the%20land%20bridge%20to%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20NATO%20commander%20James%20Stavridis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-nato-chief-war-ukraine-end-just-like-korean-war-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Convictions%2C%20'No%20Support%20From%20Activists'%20as%20Sharjeel%20Imam%20Spends%20Four%20Years%20in%20Jail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F24192815%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-24T192755.811.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJanuary%2028%2C%202024%2C%20marks%20four%20years%20in%20jail%20for%20Sharjeel%20Imam%2C%20IIT-graduate-turned-PhD-scholar%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImam%20was%20arrested%20in%202020%20after%20police%20in%20five%20different%20states%20%E2%80%93%20Assam%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20filed%20first%20information%20reports%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20speeches%20he%20made%20during%20the%20protests%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20the%20National%20Register%20for%20Citizens%20(NRC).%20Among%20other%20charges%2C%20he%20was%20charged%20under%20sedition%20and%20subsequently%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20also%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImam%20has%20spent%20four%20years%20in%20jail%2C%20despite%20not%20being%20convicted%20in%20any%20of%20the%20cases.%20Of%20the%20total%20eight%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20he%20has%20been%20given%20bail%20in%20five%2C%20never%20been%20arrested%20in%20one%2C%20and%20has%20only%20the%20UAPA%20cases%20against%20him%20remaining.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20four%20years%20have%20also%20seen%20his%20bail%20petitions%20pending%20in%20various%20Delhi%20courts%2C%20including%20one%20petition%20filed%20last%20year%20in%20which%20he%20has%20sought%20immediate%20bail%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20he%20has%20completed%20more%20than%20half%20the%20maximum%20punishment%20(seven%20years)%20under%20Section%2013%20of%20UAPA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFour%20years%20of%20his%20life%20have%20been%20wasted.%20If%20he%20was%20out%2C%20he%20could%20have%20studied%20more%2C%20he%20could%20have%20researched%20more.%20He%20is%20yet%20to%20complete%20his%20PhD.%20But%20his%20morale%20is%20not%20low.%20He%20keeps%20smiling%20and%20gives%20our%20mother%20hope%20as%20well%20saying%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Ammi%2C%20sab%20thik%20ho%20jayega%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Mother%2C%20everything%20will%20be%20alright)%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20younger%20brother%20Muzammil%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20any%20political%20prisoner%20who%20is%20in%20jail%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20stability%20is%20lost%20for%20their%20family.%20For%20my%20mother%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20In%20a%20way%20life%20has%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20since%20that%20sense%20of%20stability%20is%20lost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20years%20since%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20has%20listed%20Imam%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelayed-justice-alleged-violation-constitutional-rights-quest-bail-delhi-riots-accused%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E46%20times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20is%20now%20set%20to%20hear%20his%20plea%20afresh%20next%20month%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20case%20under%20FIR%2059%2F2020.%20His%20bail%20plea%20under%20the%20first%20FIR%2020%2F2020%20under%20which%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20his%20speeches%2C%20will%20also%20begin%20afresh%20next%20month%20in%20a%20lower%20court%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuzammil%20said%20that%20when%20Imam%20went%20to%20jail%2C%20the%20family%20knew%20that%20it%20would%20probably%20take%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20for%20him%20to%20get%20bail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20did%20not%20think%20it%20would%20go%20on%20for%20so%20many%20years.%20After%20his%20arrest%2C%20the%20north%20east%20Delhi%20riots%20took%20place.%20Yet%20he%20was%20implicated%20in%20that%20for%20no%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Muzammil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharjeel-imam-speech%5C%22%3EWhat%20Sharjeel%20Imam%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Seditious%E2%80%99%20Speech%20Has%20in%20Common%20with%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJudicial%20delays%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20his%20counsel%20Ahmad%20Ibrahim%2C%20Imam%20was%20arrested%20on%20January%2028%2C%202020%20just%20days%20after%20his%20speech%20at%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20during%20the%20CAA-NRC%20protest%20in%20which%20he%20asked%20for%20Assam%20to%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsedition-case-jnu-student-sharjeel-imam%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ccut%20off%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Efrom%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20speech%20is%20dated%20January%2016%20but%20went%20viral%20on%20January%2025%2C%202020.%20By%20January%2026%2C%202020%20there%20were%20five%20FIRs%20registered%20against%20him%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Assam%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Manipur.%20Two%20days%20later%20on%20January%2028%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20by%20Delhi%20police%20when%20he%20was%20going%20to%20surrender%20along%20with%20his%20counsel%20in%20connection%20to%20the%20Delhi%20FIR.%20Some%20months%20later%20when%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20case%20was%20registered%20he%20was%20named%20in%20the%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20with%20Umar%20Khalid%20in%20the%20FIR%2059%2F2020.%20He%20was%20also%20made%20an%20accused%20in%20two%20more%20cases-which%20relate%20to%20the%20violence%20near%20Jamia%20Milia%20University%20in%20December%202019.%20Of%20the%20total%20eight%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20he%20has%20got%20bail%20in%20five%2C%20never%20arrested%20in%20one%20and%20only%20the%20UAPA%20cases%20against%20him%20remain%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ibrahim%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20he%20has%20been%20charged%20under%20Section%2013%20of%20the%20UAPA%20in%20FIR%2022%2F2020%2C%20he%20faces%20multiple%20charges%20under%20the%20UAPA%20in%20FIR%2059%2F2020%20which%20relates%20to%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20August%20last%20year%2C%20Imam%20moved%20court%20seeking%20immediate%20bail%20under%20Section%20436A%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CRPC)%20in%20connection%20with%20FIR%2022%2F2020%20in%20which%20he%20has%20been%20charged%20under%20Section%2013%20of%20the%20UAPA%20along%20with%20124A%20(sedition)%20and%20153A%2C%20153B%2C%20505%20of%20IPC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20bail%20application%2C%20he%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Estated%20that%20the%20sedition%20proceedings%20had%20been%20stayed%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20in%202022%20put%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffull-text-what-the-supreme-court-said-while-putting-the-sedition-law-on-hold%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehold%20on%20the%20sedition%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20application%20states%20that%20bail%20is%20sought%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20had%20completed%20a%20period%20of%203%20years%20and%20more%20than%206%20months%20under%20incarceration%20and%20has%20undergone%20incarceration%20extending%20up%20to%20one-half%20of%20the%20maximum%20period%20of%20imprisonment%20specified%20for%20the%20concerned%20offence%20by%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsharjeel-imam-discharged-2019-jamia-violence-case%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Scapegoats%E2%80%99%3A%20Delhi%20Court%20Discharges%20Sharjeel%20Imam%2C%2010%20Others%20From%202019%20Jamia%20Violence%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImam%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Ibrahim%20said%20that%20his%20bail%20plea%20under%20Section%20436A%20has%20been%20pending%20for%20over%20four%20months%20as%20the%20judgement%20was%20not%20passed%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20including%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20presiding%20judge%20Amitabh%20Rawat%20whose%20transfer%20was%20announced%20in%20December%20and%20said%20in%20the%20last%20date%20of%20hearing%20that%20the%20next%20judge%20will%20hear%20the%20matter%20afresh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20it%20is%20statutory%20bail%2C%20as%20he%20has%20completed%20half%20the%20maximum%20punishment%2C%20still%20he%20has%20not%20been%20given%20bail.%20Now%20on%20February%207%20the%20matter%20has%20been%20listed%20in%20front%20of%20another%20judge%20who%20will%20consider%20the%20matter%20afresh%20and%20then%20pass%20an%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ibrahim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20bail%20under%20FIR%2059%2F2020%20is%20pending%20before%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20for%20twenty%20months%20now%20and%20has%20been%20listed%20for%20hearing%20on%20February%2022.%20His%20regular%20bail%20under%20FIR%2022%2F2020%20is%20also%20pending%20before%20high%20court%20but%20when%20he%20completed%20half%20the%20punishment%20we%20requested%20the%20court%20that%20let%20me%20get%20released%20on%20interim%20bail%20under%20Section%20436A%20but%20that%20also%20was%20not%20granted%20and%20were%20asked%20to%20approach%20the%20trial%20court.%20So%20we%20approached%20the%20lower%20court%20where%20again%20the%20matter%20was%20kept%20pending%20for%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20hopeful%20somewhere%20some%20judge%20will%20pass%20the%20order%20where%20bail%20is%20a%20mandatory%20provision%20under%20Section%20436A%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Delhi-based%20advocate%20Sarim%20Naved%2C%20delays%20in%20deciding%20bail%20petitions%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctragedy%E2%80%9D%20that%20goes%20against%20criminal%20jurisprudence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20tragedy%2C%20no%20bail%20application%20should%20be%20pending%20for%20two%20years.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20the%20person%20is%20suited%20for%20bail%20then%20please%20dismiss%20it%20so%20the%20person%20can%20try%20their%20luck%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20or%20a%20higher%20court.%20But%20keeping%20a%20bail%20application%20pending%20for%20two%20years%20is%20contrary%20to%20all%20expectations%20from%20criminal%20jurisprudence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-prison-for-sedition-sharjeel-imam-explains-his-idea-of-india%5C%22%3EIn%20Prison%20for%20%E2%80%98Sedition%E2%80%99%2C%20Sharjeel%20Imam%20Explains%20His%20Idea%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Delay%20thanks%20to%20directions%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuzammil%20said%20that%20the%20delays%20show%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjudiciary%20is%20working%20under%20government%20pressure%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20delay%20is%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20government.%20The%20judicial%20system%20is%20working%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20the%20government.%20This%20is%20not%20happening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India.%20This%20used%20to%20happen%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%20as%20well%20and%20now%20it%20is%20happening%20under%20the%20BJP.%20His%20(Sharjeel%20Imam%E2%80%99s)%20bail%20hearing%20has%20been%20postponed%2046%20times%20across%20two%20years%20in%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20cases%2C%20this%20clearly%20shows%20that%20this%20is%20political%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuzammil%20said%20that%20unlike%20other%20political%20prisoners%2C%20like%20Khalid%2C%20Imam%20has%20not%20received%20support%20from%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20prominent%20political%20activists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20choose%20people%20who%20they%20want%20to%20support%20and%20who%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSharjeel%20has%20been%20absent%20from%20posters%20of%20all%20leading%20organisations.%20I%20am%20not%20generalising%20but%20the%20general%20approach%20in%20all%20organisations%20is%20that%20they%20want%20to%20victimise%20the%20person%20who%20is%20behind%20bars.%20My%20brother%20is%20not%20a%20victim.%20He%20is%20a%20fighter%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20victimise%20him.%20We%20are%20not%20extraordinary.%20But%20we%20want%20to%20fight%20back%20on%20facts.%20Sharjeel%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20talking%2C%20his%20speeches%20have%20always%20been%20different.%20Umar%20Khalid%20has%20a%20lobby%20behind%20him.%20But%20Sharjeel%20was%20just%20a%20person%20who%20nobody%20knew%20before%20CAA-NRC.%20He%20was%20just%20a%20person%20who%20was%20doing%20his%20PhD%20from%20JNU.%20He%20had%20no%20lobby%20behind%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20jail%2C%20Muzammil%20said%20Imam%20has%20been%20reading%20legal%20books%20to%20study%20the%20law%20and%20has%20also%20taken%20to%20helping%20other%20underprivileged%20undertrials%20in%20helping%20them%20get%20legal%20aid%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20access%20to%20legal%20recourse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20keep%20hope%20that%20someday%20he%20will%20come%20out.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20that%20someone%E2%80%99s%20life%E2%80%99s%20precious%20years%20are%20getting%20wasted.%20They%20can%20keep%20postponing%20his%20bail%20but%20how%20long%20will%20they%20keep%20him%20in%20jail%3F%20As%20the%20saying%20goes%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%98Har%20urooj%20ka%20zawal%20dekhna%20hota%20hai%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(every%20rise%20has%20a%20fall).%E2%80%99%20This%20will%20be%20true%20for%20us%20as%20well%20as%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706500644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F24192815%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-24T192755.811.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2