Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68122706.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22X%20blocks%20searches%20for%20Taylor%20Swift%20after%20explicit%20AI%20images%20of%20her%20go%20viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706463774000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FCF56%2Fproduction%2F_132487035_gettyimages-1917155488.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68123671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twitter%20says%20the%20move%20is%20to%20prioritise%20safety%2C%20after%20fake%20explicit%20images%20of%20the%20singer%20went%20viral.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A461%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68123671%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68123671.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68123671.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Keeping%20Post%20Vacant%20For%2015%20Months%2C%20China%20May%20Appoint%20New%20Envoy%20to%20India%20Soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28214931%2FIndia-and-China.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20China%20may%20finally%20have%20a%20new%20ambassador%20in%20India%20early%20this%20year%2C%20with%20Beijing%20reportedly%20having%20selected%20a%20two-time%20envoy%20to%20fill%20the%20post%2C%20which%20has%20been%20lying%20vacant%20for%20over%2015%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20China%20has%20finalised%20one%20of%20its%20assistant%20foreign%20ministers%20posted%20at%20headquarters%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Xu%20Feihong%2C%20as%20the%20next%20ambassador%20to%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20no%20official%20confirmation%20from%20either%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%20or%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EXu%20is%20currently%20assistant%20minister%20for%20financial%20and%20administrative%20affairs%20in%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20side%20has%20been%20conveyed%20about%20the%20candidate%2C%20as%20per%20informed%20sources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20was%20earlier%20expected%20that%20he%20could%20be%20arriving%20as%20early%20as%20around%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Spring%20Festival%20next%20month%2C%20it%20is%20uncertain%20if%20that%20timeline%20is%20feasible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EXu%E2%80%99s%20position%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mfa.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Fziliao_674904%2Fwjrw_674925%2F202102%2Ft20210218_9881048.shtml%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eassistant%20foreign%20minister%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20the%20rank%20of%20additional%20secretary%20in%20the%20MEA.%20Since%20the%20post%20of%20Chinese%20ambassador%20to%20India%20is%20of%20the%20vice-minister%20rank%2C%20he%20would%20need%20to%20be%20promoted%20before%20he%20comes%20to%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20previous%20two%20Chinese%20ambassadors%20to%20India%2C%20Sun%20Weidong%20and%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Lui%20Zhaohui%2C%20had%20significant%20experience%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20including%20prior%20postings%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Lu%20Yucheng%2C%20who%20preceded%20Lui%2C%20did%20not%20have%20any%20regional%20experience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%2037%20years%20as%20a%20Chinese%20diplomat%2C%20Xu%E2%80%99s%20only%20assignment%20in%20South%20Asia%20was%20as%20ambassador%20to%20Afghanistan%20from%202010%20to%202013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20his%20postings%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Western%20world%2C%20ranging%20from%20Finland%20to%20Australia%2C%20with%20a%20specialisation%20in%20Europe.%20His%20last%20ambassadorial%20posting%20had%20been%20in%20Romania%20from%202015%20to%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20latest%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Sun%20Weidong%2C%20left%20his%20post%20in%20October%202022%20after%20three%20years%20that%20saw%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20Asian%20neighbours%20plummet%20following%20fatal%20clashes%20in%20the%20mountainous%20heights%20of%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20April-May%202020%2C%20India%20and%20China%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20military%20stand-off%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20their%20long%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20claimed%20that%20Chinese%20troops%20had%20moved%20further%20beyond%20their%20traditional%20positions%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%2C%20resulting%20in%20multiple%20skirmishes%20with%20the%20patrolling%20teams%20of%20the%20Indian%20army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deadliest%20conflict%20took%20place%20on%20June%2015%2C%20when%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20engaged%20in%20a%20hand-to-hand%20fight%20at%20the%20Galwan%20valley%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-acknowledges-casualties-galwan-clash-india-army%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efour%20Chinese%20troops%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20at%20least%2020%20rounds%20of%20military-level%20talks%20and%2013%20rounds%20of%20foreign%20office-led%20discussions%20have%20been%20held%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20had%20led%20to%20disengagement%20at%20five%20friction%20points%20at%20the%20Pangong%20Tso%20lake%E2%80%99s%20north%20and%20south%20banks%2C%20patrolling%20points%2015%20and%2017A%20at%20the%20Gogra-Hot%20Springs%20area%20and%20Galwan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20ambassador%20Sun%20left%20in%202022%2C%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang%20were%20the%20remaining%20areas%20of%20stand-off.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFifteen%20months%20on%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20change%20on%20this%20front.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20maintains%20that%20the%20standoff%20will%20only%20be%20resolved%20once%20there%20is%20disengagement%20and%20de-escalation%20at%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang.%20In%20contrast%2C%20China%20asserts%20that%20the%20alteration%20in%20status%20quo%20after%20May%202020%20does%20not%20encompass%20these%20two%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20has%20repeatedly%20called%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnormalisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20ties%20and%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20border%20dispute%2C%20but%20India%20insists%20that%20the%20stand-off%20has%20to%20be%20resolved%20first.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObservers%20interpret%20the%20prolonged%20delay%20in%20appointing%20another%20Chinese%20envoy%20to%20the%20Indian%20capital%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20holds%20a%20senior%20rank%20and%20would%20have%20enough%20takers%2C%20as%20a%20deliberate%20signal%20of%20displeasure%20from%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20border%20issue%2C%20there%20had%20been%20other%20issues%20over%20which%20Beijing%20has%20expressed%20its%20annoyance%2C%20like%20the%20financial%20investigations%20of%20major%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20India.%20China%20had%20also%20not%20been%20happy%20when%20India%20had%20turned%20the%20SCO%20summit%20into%20a%20virtual%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20president%20Xi%20Jinping%20also%20skipped%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20India%2C%20despite%20having%20gone%20to%20Indonesia%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%201962%20war%2C%20both%20countries%20exchanged%20ambassadors%20only%20after%20a%20gap%20of%2015%20years%20in%201976.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%20has%20usually%20been%20only%20a%20short%20gap%20of%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20at%20the%20most%20between%20ambassadors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706459298000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28214931%2FIndia-and-China.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-may-appoint-new-ambassador-to-india-soon%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20has%20learnt%20that%20China%20has%20finalised%20one%20of%20its%20assistant%20foreign%20ministers%20posted%20at%20headquarters%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Xu%20Feihong%2C%20as%20the%20next%20ambassador%20to%20India.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-may-appoint-new-ambassador-to-india-soon%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Three%20US%20troops%20killed%20and%2034%20injured%20in%20drone%20attack%20in%20Jordan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706458740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F70x70%2Fskynews-jordan-united-states_6436207.jpg%3F20240128164758%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthree-us-troops-killed-and-25-injured-in-drone-attack-in-jordan-13058827%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20American%20troops%20have%20been%20killed%20and%2034%20injured%20in%20a%20drone%20attack%20in%20Jordan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1088%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fthree-us-troops-killed-and-25-injured-in-drone-attack-in-jordan-13058827%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthree-us-troops-killed-and-25-injured-in-drone-attack-in-jordan-13058827%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fthree-us-troops-killed-and-25-injured-in-drone-attack-in-jordan-13058827%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Simultaneous%20Elections%20High-Level%20Committee%20Holds%20Its%20Fourth%20Meeting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26110403%2FThe-Wire-56.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20who%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20high-level%20committee%20on%20simultaneous%20elections%20at%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20state%20and%20municipal%20levels%2C%20has%20held%20consultations%20with%20prominent%20lawyers%2C%20including%20former%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20he%20held%20consultations%20with%20are%20Justice%20U.U.%20Lalit%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%3B%20Justice%20Sanjib%20Banerjee%2C%20former%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Madras%20high%20court%3B%20as%20well%20as%20Manan%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Bar%20Council%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKovind%20also%20met%20Deepak%20Pandurang%20Dhavalikar%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Maharastrawadi%20Gomantak%20Party%2C%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20political%20parties%20are%20not%20in%20support%20of%20the%20proposition%2C%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20deeply%20centralising%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20national%20parties%2C%2033%20state%20parties%20and%20seven%20registered%20unrecognised%20parties%20have%20been%20formally%20written%20to%20and%20asked%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%20was%20termed%20an%20%E2%80%9Cundemocratic%E2%80%9D%20idea%20%E2%80%9Cagainst%20%5Bthe%5D%20basic%20structure%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20Constitution%E2%80%9D%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20earlier%20this%20month.%20He%20said%20the%20panel%20on%20this%20must%20be%20dissolved%20and%20the%20idea%20abandoned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fone-nation-one-election-an-undemocratic-idea-against-basic-structure-of-constitution-kharge-to-kovind-panel-9117337%2F%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20sake%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Crobust%20democracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D2000148%5C%22%3Efourth%20meeting%20of%20the%20high-level%20committee%20was%20also%20held%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%20(January%2027).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20representative%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20this%20committee%2C%20with%20Congress%20leader%20and%20MP%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20having%20refused%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20Kovind%20said%20that%20polls%20being%20held%20concurrently%20at%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20levels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fone-nation-one-election-in-national-interest-nothing-to-do-with-any-party-ram-nath-kovind%2Farticle67557721.ece%5C%22%3Eis%20in%20the%20national%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20it%20would%20benefit%20whichever%20party%20was%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20it%20BJP%20or%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20November%2021%2C%202023%2C%20Chowdhury%20had%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cparty%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20requesting%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20cooperate%20as%20this%20is%20in%20the%20national%20interest.%20No%20political%20party%20has%20got%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kovind%20told%20the%20media%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20a%20public%20notice%2C%20the%20high-level%20committee%20had%20called%20for%20suggestions%2C%20and%20said%20those%20received%20by%20January%2015%20would%20be%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20leader%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20who%20is%20also%20former%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3B%20N.K.%20Singh%2C%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%3B%20Subhash%20C.%20Kashyap%2C%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%3B%20Sanjay%20Kothari%2C%20former%20chief%20vigilance%20commissioner%20and%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20senior%20advocate%20attended%20the%20meeting%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20government%20release%20on%20the%20meeting%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20presentation%20was%20made%20before%20the%20committee%20based%20on%20the%20research%20paper%20%E2%80%98Macroeconomic%20Impact%20of%20Harmonizing%20Electoral%20Cycles%2C%20Evidences%20from%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20co-authored%20by%20N.K%20Singh%20and%20Prachi%20Mishra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20also%20decided%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20conversation%20process%20with%20stakeholders%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20argument%20of%20%E2%80%98cost-saving%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20critiqued%20by%20the%20Congress%20already%20when%20Kharge%20wrote%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20committee%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ECI%20had%20estimated%20the%20cost%20of%20conducting%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20VVPAT%20machines%20to%20be%20about%20Rs%203%2C870%20crore%20%E2%80%A6%20The%20argument%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20conducting%20elections%20is%20extremely%20high%20seems%20baseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20elections%20are%20held%20once%20in%20five%20years%2C%20the%20expenses%20make%20up%20less%20than%200.02%25%20of%20the%20total%20Union%20budget%20for%20the%20preceding%20five%20years.%20When%20elections%20are%20held%20separately%20to%20the%20state%20assemblies%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20election%20is%20fully%20borne%20by%20the%20respective%20states.%20The%20expenses%20for%20assembly%20elections%20may%20also%20be%20a%20similar%20percentage%20of%20their%20state%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20the%20people%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20consider%20this%20small%20amount%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20to%20uphold%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI(M)%20has%20also%20written%20to%20the%20committee%20registering%20its%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20objection%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98ONOE%E2%80%99%20is%20being%20%E2%80%9Csought%20to%20be%20imposed%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20consideration%20of%20the%20proposal%20itself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fcpim-calls-one-nation-one-election-inherently-anti-democratic-in-letter-to-kovind-led-panel-2839525%5C%22%3Eruns%20against%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fgovt-committee-simultaneous-elections-explained-8918921%2F%5C%22%3Ein%202015%2C%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20compiled%20a%20report%20on%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20at%20the%20time%20told%20the%20committee%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cimpractical%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunworkable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20called%20the%20report%20anti-democratic%20and%20unconstitutional%2C%20while%20the%20CPI%20and%20the%20NCP%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20feasible%E2%80%9D.%20The%20CPI(M)%20also%20highlighted%20%E2%80%9Cpractical%20problems%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsimultaneous-elections-panel-suggestions-9096160%2F%5C%22%3EKovind-led%20committee%E2%80%99s%20terms%20of%20reference%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexamine%20and%20make%20recommendations%20for%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%20(Lok%20Sabha)%2C%20State%20Legislative%20Ass