20murdered%20the%20gathbandhan.%20The%20public%20will%20give%20their%20reply.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20also%20said%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%E2%80%9D%20and%20congratulated%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CINDIA%20alliance%20is%20strong.%20Whatever%20happens%2C%20happens%20for%20the%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20party%20knew%20about%20his%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20impending%20exit%20and%20the%20country%20had%20seen%20many%20%E2%80%9Caayaram%20gayaram%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20received%20this%20information%20from%20Laluji%20and%20Tejashwi%20that%20he%20(Kumar)%20would%20leave%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20stay%20together%20and%20fight%20together.%20If%20he%20wants%20to%20stay%20with%20us%2C%20he%20will%2C%20but%20he%20wants%20to%20go%20if%20he%20will.%20We%20had%20this%20information%20but%20to%20keep%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20intact%20we%20did%20not%20say%20anything%20to%20not%20give%20out%20the%20wrong%20message.%20That%20is%20why%20over%20the%20last%20two%20days%20we%20are%20seeing%20the%20developments.%20But%20we%20had%20the%20information%20from%20the%20Bihar%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20Lalu%20Prasad.%20And%20today%20this%20has%20come%20true.%20But%20this%20country%20has%20many%20such%20%E2%80%98aayaram%20gayaram%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Nitish%20said%20that%20the%20reason%20behind%20his%20exit%20was%20things%20not%20working%20out%20with%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20occasion%20came%20because%20things%20were%20not%20working%20out.%20I%20had%20stopped%20saying%20anything.%20We%20took%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20views%20into%20account%20including%20my%20party.%20We%20were%20working%20on%20an%20alliance%20(INDIA)%20for%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20but%20things%20were%20not%20working%20out.%20Now%2C%20we%20will%20form%20a%20new%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20media%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20Kumar%2C%20who%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20chief%20architect%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20is%20giving%20tough%20competition%20to%20%E2%80%9Cchameleons%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20frequently%20changes%20political%20partners%2C%20is%20giving%20tough%20competition%20to%20the%20chameleons%20in%20changing%20colours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9D%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%B6%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%97%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%82%E0%A5%A4%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B8%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%98%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9E%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0