ay%20evening%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fayaram-gayaram-politics-of-nitish-at-play-poised-to-rejoin-nda%5C%22%3Eknown%20for%20his%20regular%20shifts%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20alliances.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20RJD%20was%20in%20the%20dark%20when%20he%20suddenly%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Mahagathbandhan.%20Then%2C%20when%20he%20left%20the%20BJP%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20too%20had%20no%20clue%2C%20until%20he%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20again%20switch%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK.C.%20Tyagi%2C%20JD(U)%20spokesperson%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20placed%20the%20blame%20squarely%20on%20the%20Congress%20for%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20caucus%20of%20the%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20steal%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20meeting%20that%20took%20place%20on%20December%2019%2C%20through%20a%20conspiracy%2C%20to%20get%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20proposed%20(as%20chairperson%20for%20the%20alliance).%20Earlier%20in%20the%20meeting%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20it%20was%20unanimously%20decided%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20work%20together%20without%20any%20face.%20The%20Congress%20caucus%20suggested%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20name%20through%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20(West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20and%20TMC%20chief).%20All%20INDIA%20alliance%20parties%20whether%20it%20is%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20TMC%20or%20SP%20they%20have%20all%20defeated%20the%20Congress%20and%20have%20made%20their%20own%20identity%20by%20fighting%20against%20Congress.%20Congress%20kept%20dragging%20the%20seat%20sharing%2C%20we%20kept%20saying%20that%20seat%20sharing%20needs%20to%20happen%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETyagi%20has%20earlier%20also%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20starting%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctiming%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Yatra%20was%20not%20right%2C%20and%20if%20a%20yatra%20had%20to%20be%20planned%2C%20it%20should%20have%20been%20one%20including%20all%20alliance%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20served%20another%20blow%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20earlier%20this%20week%20when%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20announced%20that%20the%20TMC%20would%20fight%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20its%20own%20at%20least%20in%20Bengal%2C%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20somersaults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNitish%20Kumar%20is%20known%20for%20his%20political%20somersaults%20at%20regular%20intervals.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20he%20has%20decided%20to%20quit%20the%20opposition%20grouping%20INDIA%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20NDA.%20The%20people%20will%20give%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20such%20political%20opportunism%2C%E2%80%9D%20TMC%20MP%20Sougata%20Roy%20said%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20alliance%20partner%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20took%20aim%20at%20the%20BJP%C2%A0%20for%20joining%20hands%20with%20%E2%80%9Cpalturam%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20Ram%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20Palturam%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20BJP%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20himself%20had%20called%20him%20Palturam%20when%20Nitish%20Kumar%20had%20joined%20hands%20with%20Lalu.%20Shah%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20doors%20are%20closed%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20They%20talk%20about%20Ram%20and%20Ram%20Rajya%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20they%20join%20hands%20with%20Palturam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livehindustan.com%2Fnational%2Fstory-nitish-kumar-biggest-palturam-sanjay-raut-on-bihar-crisis-9250915.html%5C%22%3Equoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%E2%80%99s%20T.K.S.%20Elangovan%20said%20that%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20exit%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbreak%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20kind%20of%20pressure%20he%20is%20facing%20from%20the%20BJP.%20BJP%20wants%20to%20break%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20because%20they%20are%20afraid%20they%20might%20lose%20the%20elections.%20They%20have%20particularly%20chosen%20Bihar%20by%20convincing%20Nitish%20Kumar%20that%20Lalu%20Prasad%20may%20become%20CM%20because%20there%20is%20another%20strong%20regional%20party%20there.%20That%20might%20be%20used%20against%20Lalu%20Prasad%20since%20both%20of%20them%20are%20in%20the%20same%20alliance%2C%20and%20Nitish%20may%20lose%20his%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20berth%20seat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706444198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30172607%2FF6h-A1CXQAAeurW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-strong-says-opposition-block-as-nitish-kumar-rejoins-hands-with-nda%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RJD%E2%80%99s%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20said%20that%20the%20public%20will%20give%20a%20befitting%20reply%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20said%20that%20there%20have%20been%20many%20%E2%80%98Aayaram%2C%20Gayaram%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A32%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-strong-says-opposition-block-as-nitish-kumar-rejoins-hands-with-nda%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20warship%20shoots%20down%20Houthi%20drone%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706443560000%2C%22vi