ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Frahul-gandhi-stopped-from-visiting-assam-temple-batadrava-than-2491803-2024-01-22%5C%22%3Edenied%3C%2Fa%3E%20entry%20into%20the%20pilgrimage%20site%2C%20Gandhi%20wryly%20told%20reporters%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20one%20person%20is%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20temple%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20taking%20a%20potshot%20at%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20whose%20presence%20at%20the%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20ritual%20was%20telecast%20by%20all%20media%20channels%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20visuals%2C%20one%20from%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20other%20from%20Assam%2C%20underline%20the%20crossroads%20where%20our%20country%20stands%2C%20months%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20appropriation%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20leaves%20no%20doubt%20about%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20election%20pitch%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20elections%20have%20somewhat%20rightly%20become%20the%20benchmark%20for%20assessing%20the%20influence%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20ideology%2C%20the%20ongoing%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20proves%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20fair%20to%20gauge%20its%20success%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20election%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20argue%20that%20despite%20the%20Yatra%20passing%20through%20states%20such%20as%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20lost%20the%20states%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20here%E2%80%99s%20a%20counter%20argument.%20A%20look%20at%20the%20states%20through%20which%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20is%20passing%20through%20reveals%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20much%20more%20to%20the%20initiative%20than%20just%20winning%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yo