hen%20she%20was%2018.%20Enjoying%20with%20her%20friends%20on%20a%20Puducherry%20beach%2C%20she%20suddenly%20fell%20down%20while%20playing%20in%20the%20water.%20A%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20left%20her%20without%20any%20feeling%20under%20the%20neck.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20unwavering%20love%20and%20support%20of%20her%20parents%2C%20and%20her%20incredible%20resilience%2C%20she%20emerged%20like%20a%20phoenix%2C%20and%20today%20provides%20wings%20to%20hundreds%20of%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20through%20her%20venture%20%E2%80%98Soulfree%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoulfree%20INSPIRE%20(Integrated%20Spinal%20Rehabilitation%20Centre)%20in%202013%2C%20the%20trust%E2%80%99s%20rehab%20centre%2C%20provides%20holistic%20treatment%2C%20rehabilitation%2C%20medical%20care%2C%20education%2C%20counselling%2C%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20persons%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries%20for%20free.%20The%2020%2C000%20square%20feet%20facility%20in%20Tiruvannamalai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20has%20helped%20over%20200%20people%20with%20severe%20disabilities%20live%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESwimming%20against%20the%20tide%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201074px)%20100vw%2C%201074px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Preethi%20has%20helped%20over%202500%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152.jpg%201074w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152-300x175.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152-500x292.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152-768x449.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-12-1705936152-150x88.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338800%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPreethi%20has%20helped%20over%202500%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20accident%2C%20Preethi%20was%20in%20shock%20and%20faced%20a%20really%20tough%20time.%20From%20excelling%20in%20all%20spheres%20of%20life%2C%20being%20confined%20to%20a%20wheelchair%20broke%20her%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20heart%20was%20totally%20broken.%20I%20had%20a%20privileged%20existence%20for%20the%20first%2018%20years%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20showered%20with%20love%20at%20home%2C%20was%20in%20the%20top%202%20percent%20of%20students%20in%20America%2C%20played%20cricket%20with%20legends%2C%20was%20extremely%20fit%20and%20beautiful.%20I%20was%20making%20my%20way%20towards%20success%2C%20when%20the%20accident%20left%20me%20in%20complete%20shock%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preethi%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20from%20being%20able%20to%20throw%20the%20ball%20with%20full%20force%2C%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20even%20move%20her%20little%20finger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20being%20extraordinary%20in%20every%20way%2C%20I%20suddenly%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20feed%20myself%2C%20bathe%20myself.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20get%20out%20of%20bed.%20It%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337346%2Fdisability-inspiring-veena-ambarish-kari-dosa-food-cart-bengaluru-jp-nagar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereally%20broke%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20stood%20by%20her%20like%20rock