0to%20get%20a%20formal%20degree.%20She%20took%20up%20BSc%20Medical%20Sociology%20as%20it%20had%20no%20practical%20exams.%20She%20also%20did%20MSc%20in%20Psychology%20despite%20wanting%20to%20do%20counselling%20psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20counsel%20people%20as%20my%20voice%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20have.%20I%20was%20denied%20admission%20and%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20psychology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20too%20deserve%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rehabilitation%20is%20provided%20free%20of%20cost%20at%20Soulfree%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338795%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERehabilitation%20is%20provided%20free%20of%20cost%20at%20Soulfree%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20as%20she%20grappled%20with%20getting%20an%20education%20and%20a%20treatment%20for%20her%20mother%2C%20she%20encountered%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337564%2Ffree-tiffin-service-meals-for-senior-citizens-rakesh-panchal-gujarat-donate-now%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20deaths%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20shook%20her%20to%20the%20core.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20wanting%20to%20take%20care%20of%20them%2C%20two%20paraplegic%20girls%20who%20I%20knew%20were%20apparentfly%20poisoned%20by%20their%20families.%20It%20left%20me%20wondering%2C%20India%20has%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20populations%20and%20yet%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20a%20quadriplegic%20or%20a%20paraplegic%20person%20to%20live%20with%20dignity.%20There%20was%20no%20one%20to%20take%20care%20of%20me%20when%20my%20mom%20got%20sick%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20started%20researching%20and%20found%20that%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20many%20long-term%20rehabilitation%20centres%20or%20places%20that%20offered%20care%20for%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries.%20Her%20mother%20then%20persuaded%20her%20to%20start%20such%20a%20haven%20that%20provides%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20for%20people%20with%20severe%20disabilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20I%20laughed%20off%20the%20idea%20as%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20about%20running%20or%20financing%20a%20non-profit%20organisation.%20But%20the%20death%20of%20these%20girls%20made%20me%20wake%20up.%20If%20I%20am%20just%20going%20to%20be%20afraid%20to%20do%20something%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%20No%20one%20understands%20this%20better%20than%20me%20due%20to%20my%20lived%20experience.%20I%20decided%20to%20raise%20my%20voice%20and%20do%20whatever%20I%20can%20to%20somehow%20uplift%20this%20segment%20of%20society%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20so%20completely%20invisible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20she%20started%20Soulfree%20Inspire.%20People%20come%20with%20a%20caregiver%20and%20spend%20about%206%20months%20in%20the%20centre.%20They%20receive%20training%2C%20which%20Preethi%20calls%20re-engineering%2C%20where%20they%20get%20emotional%20and%20physical%20rehabilitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20restore%20their%20will%20to%20live.%20Our%20aim%20is%20to%20restore%20self-reliance%20from%20a%20physiological%2C%20psychological%20and%20socio%20economic%20perspective.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20them%20to%20go%20home%20and%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20some%20money.%20We%20are%20giving%20international%20standards%20of%20care%20free%20of%20cost.%20We%20have%20physiotherapy%2C%20occupational%20therapy%2C%20hydrotherapy%2C%20sports%2C%20counselling%20sessions%2C%20training%20sessions%2C%20tailoring%2C%20computer%20classes%20and%20more.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20holistic%20system%20born%20from%20an%20experiential%20framework%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Preethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoulfree%20also%20offers%20knowledge%20and%20awareness%20programs%20about%20spinal%20cord%20injury.%20They%20have%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20women%20and%20provide%20a%20support%20system%20to%20those%20with%20severe%20disabilities%20through%20educational%20and%20employment%20opportunities.%20They%20also%20provide%20wheelchairs%20and%20medical%20care%20to%20those%20in%20need.%20To%20keep%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20spirits%20up%2C%20they%20also%20have%20conference%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthikeyan%20(25)%2C%20was%20bedridden%20after%20he%20fell%20from%20a%20tree%20three%20years%20ago.%20He%20came%20to%20Soulfree%20six%20months%20back%20and%20is%20now%20able%20to%20walk%20with%20a%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20bedridden%20made%20me%20contemplate%20ending%20my%20life.%20I%20also%20had%20some%20bedsores.%20I%20was%20using%20a%20wheelchair.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20walk%20using%20a%20stick%20and%20do%20my%20daily%20chores%20and%20have%20learnt%20tailoring%20and%20computers%2C%20which%20I%20will%20use%20to%20support%20myself%20once%20I%E2%80%99m%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Karthikeyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreethi%20is%20al