ries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20various%20activities%20that%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337937%2Fbest-budget-homestay-in-uttarakhand-the-nanda-stone-mukteshwar-by-ashish-verma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20homestay%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoffers%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20few%20activities%20at%20our%20homestays.%20We%20have%20divided%20them%20according%20to%20the%20season%20%E2%80%94%20monsoons%20and%20winters.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20related%20to%20water%20sports%20like%20Cliff%20Jumping%2C%20River%20Canyoning%2C%20Kayaking%2C%20etc.%20We%20also%20organise%20treks%20to%20explore%20the%20nearby%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20types%20of%20treks%20%E2%80%94%20short%20and%20long%20treks.%20%E2%80%9CA%20long%20trek%20is%20around%20four%20hours%20and%20a%20short%20trek%20is%20about%202%20hours%20long.%20On%20those%20treks%2C%20you%20can%20enjoy%20the%20landscapes%2C%20enjoy%20bathing%20in%204%20waterfalls%2C%20you%20can%20see%20the%20fossils%20and%20the%20magnificent%20rock%20formations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20also%20arranges%20cave%20exploration%20for%20the%20guests%20on%20request.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20trained%20nearly%2040%20locals%20as%20trek%20guides%20to%20help%20people%20in%20these%20treks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20exploring%20the%20wilderness%2C%20the%20homestay%20also%20organises%20village%20tours%20and%20cultural%20activities%20like%20eating%20authentic%20food.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20want%20to%20introduce%20people%20to%20our%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286536%2Ftop-eco-friendly-sustainable-ethical-indian-clothing-brands-suta-okhai-buy-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20culture%20and%20heritage.%20%3C